WEBVTT

00:00:01.944 --> 00:00:08.054
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:00:12.104 --> 00:00:15.639
As I told you yesterday,

00:00:16.797 --> 00:00:20.664
that truth is what it is.

00:00:20.865 --> 00:00:27.076
We cannot understand it,

00:00:27.441 --> 00:00:29.904
you have to feel it.

00:00:31.014 --> 00:00:34.444
We cannot conceptualize it,

00:00:34.654 --> 00:00:38.114
and you cannot feel it also

00:00:38.314 --> 00:00:41.766
at this human awareness.

00:00:44.224 --> 00:00:47.504
We have to become a subtler being,

00:00:47.764 --> 00:00:50.184
as described in all the Scriptures,

00:00:50.394 --> 00:00:53.364
that you are to be born again

00:00:53.574 --> 00:00:57.284
and that you have to become the Spirit,

00:00:57.504 --> 00:01:04.119
to feel the existence of Truth.

00:01:08.374 --> 00:01:13.433
First thing, we have to understand,

00:01:13.634 --> 00:01:16.885
that all this is a process

00:01:17.085 --> 00:01:20.093
of a living energy.

00:01:21.234 --> 00:01:24.784
Divine is a living energy,

00:01:25.024 --> 00:01:30.814
and divinity within you also is a living energy.

00:01:31.054 --> 00:01:37.484
We do not understand sometimes what is a living energy.

00:01:38.679 --> 00:01:43.019
When we sow a seed in the ground,

00:01:43.219 --> 00:01:46.533
they sprout by themselves.

00:01:46.734 --> 00:01:50.974
When a mother conceives the child,

00:01:51.175 --> 00:01:55.791
according to the normal nature of human beings,

00:01:55.992 --> 00:02:01.548
their body has to expel everything that is foreign.

00:02:01.749 --> 00:02:04.359
But when the child is conceived,

00:02:04.559 --> 00:02:08.693
it is not only kept in the body

00:02:08.894 --> 00:02:11.484
but is nourished, looked after, developed,

00:02:11.684 --> 00:02:15.614
and at the right time it is expelled.

00:02:18.224 --> 00:02:21.774
There are so many other things which cannot be explained

00:02:22.014 --> 00:02:24.814
through medical science.

00:02:26.724 --> 00:02:32.677
But one must know that to understand what I am saying,

00:02:33.384 --> 00:02:36.258
you must have an open mind,

00:02:36.458 --> 00:02:39.005
like a scientist has.

00:02:39.614 --> 00:02:42.375
And if you find what I am saying,

00:02:42.575 --> 00:02:46.123
which is like a hypothesis,

00:02:46.324 --> 00:02:51.604
is true and gives you the experience of the truth,

00:02:51.844 --> 00:02:54.966
then as honest people you must accept it,

00:02:55.189 --> 00:02:59.534
because it is for your emancipation

00:02:59.734 --> 00:03:03.561
and for the emancipation of the whole world.

00:03:04.464 --> 00:03:09.000
In our evolutionary process now we have become human beings,

00:03:09.201 --> 00:03:13.014
but as you know we have not achieved the absoluteness.

00:03:13.274 --> 00:03:17.454
For that something has to happen within us:

00:03:19.244 --> 00:03:22.474
the last breakthrough has to take place,

00:03:22.746 --> 00:03:27.878
and that is what we are talking about here.

00:03:28.804 --> 00:03:33.414
You have been already told about the mechanism that is here.

00:03:34.084 --> 00:03:37.403
And this mechanism exists within you,

00:03:37.604 --> 00:03:41.553
these two lines that you see, left and right,

00:03:41.754 --> 00:03:47.294
are nourishing our left and right sympathetic nervous system.

00:03:47.744 --> 00:03:51.044
And the central one that you see here

00:03:51.334 --> 00:03:56.167
is nourishing our parasympathetic nervous system.

00:03:57.286 --> 00:04:03.123
Now these centers are

00:04:03.324 --> 00:04:06.960
created by these two sides,

00:04:07.198 --> 00:04:10.648
left and the right like this in the center,

00:04:11.624 --> 00:04:13.984
and these centers

00:04:14.224 --> 00:04:18.773
are all the time exhausted by us

00:04:18.974 --> 00:04:22.864
whenever we try to use energy.

00:04:23.894 --> 00:04:26.404
For example, if you are running fast

00:04:26.604 --> 00:04:29.570
you can increase the heart rate,

00:04:29.771 --> 00:04:32.694
but it comes to its normal self

00:04:32.944 --> 00:04:35.604
through the parasympathetic nervous system,

00:04:35.814 --> 00:04:40.030
while in emergency you use your sympathetic nervous system.

00:04:40.736 --> 00:04:46.173
Thus, we start exhausting the energy of these centers,

00:04:46.374 --> 00:04:49.793
and that’s how we get into problems

00:04:49.994 --> 00:04:55.009
of our physical, mental and emotional being.

00:04:56.164 --> 00:04:59.279
Supposing we are exhausting the energy on the right-hand side

00:04:59.480 --> 00:05:00.884
means you are very futuristic,

00:05:01.084 --> 00:05:03.884
you are planning all the time, thinking of the future

00:05:04.164 --> 00:05:07.184
then what happens, the right side starts moving like this.

00:05:07.434 --> 00:05:11.453
And something happens on the left side, a shock, then it breaks.

00:05:11.654 --> 00:05:15.444
When it breaks, then we lose our connection

00:05:15.644 --> 00:05:17.784
with the central nervous system;

00:05:18.078 --> 00:05:21.041
that means we lose our connection with our brain that controls it

00:05:21.242 --> 00:05:23.004
and we become on our own.

00:05:23.204 --> 00:05:27.213
And that’s how psychosomatic troubles start, specially cancer,

00:05:27.414 --> 00:05:29.774
and the malignancy sets in.

00:05:30.544 --> 00:05:33.623
When the Kundalini rises from there,

00:05:33.824 --> 00:05:37.493
She goes through this center as well as this center,

00:05:37.694 --> 00:05:40.974
pushes them together and nourishes them.

00:05:41.694 --> 00:05:43.923
Now let us see

00:05:44.124 --> 00:05:47.933
what is the quality of all these centers within us.

00:05:48.134 --> 00:05:50.784
This is all within us, and we have to see

00:05:51.024 --> 00:05:55.893
that how we exist with the energy of these centers.

00:05:56.094 --> 00:06:00.964
The first center that you see is down below.

00:06:01.924 --> 00:06:04.519
This center which is down below,

00:06:04.719 --> 00:06:07.053
is below the Kundalini,

00:06:07.254 --> 00:06:11.463
and so we have to understand that

00:06:11.664 --> 00:06:16.584
this center supports the rising of the Kundalini,

00:06:16.785 --> 00:06:20.054
but it's not pierced through by the Kundalini.

00:06:20.614 --> 00:06:23.084
This center is

00:06:23.294 --> 00:06:27.306
for all our excretion,

00:06:27.507 --> 00:06:29.184
even sex.

00:06:29.384 --> 00:06:32.164
So those people who say that through sex

00:06:32.364 --> 00:06:34.054
you can raise your Kundalini,

00:06:34.255 --> 00:06:38.003
they are absolutely wrong and are misleading you.

00:06:38.204 --> 00:06:41.723
Because you can see here clearly, it is below that.

00:06:41.924 --> 00:06:45.184
This is the center of innocence,

00:06:45.774 --> 00:06:47.400
is the center

00:06:47.600 --> 00:06:50.483
where we say that the deity of innocence is sitting here,

00:06:50.684 --> 00:06:53.724
who incarnated later on as Christ

00:06:53.924 --> 00:06:55.864
on the higher center there

00:06:56.064 --> 00:06:59.444
between, where you see this [lying], my red spot,

00:06:59.704 --> 00:07:01.901
is one of the windows.

00:07:02.102 --> 00:07:05.187
It is on the optic chiasma.

00:07:06.264 --> 00:07:08.803
And that’s how we say that

00:07:09.003 --> 00:07:13.120
Christ was the incarnation of innocence.

00:07:13.321 --> 00:07:17.479
Because He is sitting on the optic chiasma,

00:07:17.680 --> 00:07:20.050
He said that,

00:07:22.064 --> 00:07:26.756
“Thou shall not have adulterous eyes”.

00:07:28.214 --> 00:07:30.764
This is the sentence He has used.

00:07:30.964 --> 00:07:33.824
To such a subtle way He has suggested

00:07:34.024 --> 00:07:37.384
that you will not have adulterous eyes,

00:07:37.584 --> 00:07:41.125
meaning you will have very pure eyes,

00:07:41.326 --> 00:07:43.283
innocent eyes.

00:07:43.484 --> 00:07:45.334
Why did He talk of the eyes?

00:07:45.534 --> 00:07:48.964
Because He’s sitting on the optic chiasma.

00:07:49.624 --> 00:07:52.304
It’s a very constricted center,

00:07:52.527 --> 00:07:55.283
and He was to be resurrected

00:07:55.484 --> 00:07:58.763
to show that you can also pass through

00:07:58.963 --> 00:08:00.783
that center very easily.

00:08:00.984 --> 00:08:05.484
So His message is not His crucifixion, but His resurrection.

00:08:05.814 --> 00:08:08.654
And that is how we are all going to resurrected,

00:08:08.854 --> 00:08:11.544
not after death, but right now.

00:08:12.424 --> 00:08:16.475
We should not postpone our resurrection any more.

00:08:17.774 --> 00:08:21.504
Then this second center that we have, is very important,

00:08:21.734 --> 00:08:24.804
which is called as the Swadisthana.

00:08:26.054 --> 00:08:29.909
This center looks after physical

00:08:30.124 --> 00:08:33.036
and our mental activities.

00:08:33.784 --> 00:08:35.414
Perhaps the doctors don’t know

00:08:35.614 --> 00:08:38.590
that it has a very important work to do,

00:08:38.791 --> 00:08:44.293
is that it has to nourish the brain

00:08:44.515 --> 00:08:48.713
with new cells,

00:08:49.274 --> 00:08:52.963
because all the time the brain is using

00:08:53.164 --> 00:08:55.264
these cells for its activity.

00:08:55.464 --> 00:08:58.864
So the energy has to go from this center,

00:08:59.104 --> 00:09:01.353
up there you can see

00:09:02.264 --> 00:09:06.223
and then it nourishes the center,

00:09:06.424 --> 00:09:09.080
it nourishes the brain

00:09:09.280 --> 00:09:11.413
through its activity.

00:09:11.614 --> 00:09:13.533
Now when we are very futuristic

00:09:13.734 --> 00:09:16.317
or we are using too much of our brain, I should say,

00:09:16.518 --> 00:09:18.424
too much of our brain activity we have,

00:09:18.624 --> 00:09:21.028
we are futuristic, we are planning too much,

00:09:21.229 --> 00:09:25.024
thinking too much, all the time thoughts and thoughts and thoughts,

00:09:25.224 --> 00:09:30.454
that time we are using the energy of this center.

00:09:30.937 --> 00:09:35.464
But this center has another very important thing to be done,

00:09:35.664 --> 00:09:37.484
that it goes round, as you see,

00:09:37.684 --> 00:09:39.424
it moves all round here

00:09:39.624 --> 00:09:43.064
is shown here directly but it’s connected to the center

00:09:43.264 --> 00:09:45.624
and it moves round and round and round,

00:09:45.824 --> 00:09:48.764
and gives energy to this area

00:09:48.964 --> 00:09:52.684
where we have our liver, our pancreas,

00:09:53.294 --> 00:09:58.864
our spleen, kidney, and parts of intestines.

00:09:59.684 --> 00:10:03.933
Now if you start exhausting ourselves with too much thinking,

00:10:04.134 --> 00:10:07.734
then the main work of this center suffers

00:10:07.934 --> 00:10:11.884
and that’s how we develop all these diseases of all these organs:

00:10:12.084 --> 00:10:15.793
like for example, with liver you develop a liver problem.

00:10:15.994 --> 00:10:19.774
Liver problem means that liver has a function

00:10:19.974 --> 00:10:24.973
to emit heat from your body, which is poison,

00:10:25.174 --> 00:10:27.864
into the bloodstream.

00:10:28.065 --> 00:10:32.774
But when liver gets upset, we should say,

00:10:32.974 --> 00:10:35.773
the heat is retained in the liver.

00:10:35.974 --> 00:10:38.361
It passes upward and downward.

00:10:38.562 --> 00:10:40.733
When it passes upward it affects

00:10:40.934 --> 00:10:44.375
a center there, as you can see, which we call as the right heart,

00:10:44.576 --> 00:10:47.963
and people develop what we call the disease as asthma.

00:10:48.164 --> 00:10:50.484
And when it passes downwards

00:10:50.684 --> 00:10:52.673
it reaches the kidneys and coagulates

00:10:52.874 --> 00:10:54.333
and you get kidney troubles,

00:10:54.534 --> 00:10:59.985
for which we have to go on dialysis and ultimately to die.

00:11:00.186 --> 00:11:06.272
So this heat is created because our liver is out of gear.

00:11:06.633 --> 00:11:09.243
At the same time this heat can also pass,

00:11:09.444 --> 00:11:12.381
if a person, say, at a very young age drinks

00:11:12.582 --> 00:11:15.781
and puts in too much of physical efforts

00:11:15.981 --> 00:11:18.811
and is all the time busy thinking, thinking,

00:11:19.012 --> 00:11:22.364
he might get a very fatal heart attack,

00:11:22.564 --> 00:11:25.094
because this heat can go towards his heart

00:11:25.294 --> 00:11:26.743
and just collapse it.

00:11:26.944 --> 00:11:29.764
Also those people work very hard like that

00:11:29.964 --> 00:11:32.377
can get a very massive heart attack.

00:11:32.578 --> 00:11:35.793
But the people who have other problems,

00:11:35.994 --> 00:11:38.710
on the left-hand side, are different type.

00:11:38.911 --> 00:11:42.197
They are the people who have lethargic organs.

00:11:42.504 --> 00:11:44.476
These organs do not work,

00:11:44.676 --> 00:11:46.453
and when they do not work

00:11:46.654 --> 00:11:48.624
then they have all the other problems

00:11:48.824 --> 00:11:50.684
of the left side, as we call it;

00:11:50.884 --> 00:11:54.463
and this also causes another serious problem

00:11:54.664 --> 00:11:56.924
of psychosomatic troubles.

00:11:57.214 --> 00:12:00.604
Now the essence of this center

00:12:00.804 --> 00:12:03.911
is that it is creativity.

00:12:05.134 --> 00:12:08.004
When the Kundalini nourishes this center,

00:12:08.214 --> 00:12:11.204
people become extremely creative.

00:12:11.424 --> 00:12:14.084
Now you have seen these artists who are playing here.

00:12:14.284 --> 00:12:17.054
They were very simple, ordinary artists,

00:12:17.254 --> 00:12:19.044
but after coming to Sahaja Yoga

00:12:19.244 --> 00:12:21.384
suddenly they have bloomed so much.

00:12:21.644 --> 00:12:23.934
The most surprising thing is that people,

00:12:24.134 --> 00:12:26.064
say, even from Switzerland

00:12:26.264 --> 00:12:28.254
who do not know a word of Sanskrit,

00:12:28.454 --> 00:12:30.309
who do not know a word of Hindi language

00:12:30.510 --> 00:12:33.944
have composed poems, they have put them to tunes,

00:12:34.144 --> 00:12:37.724
and they sing as good as these people can sing.

00:12:38.084 --> 00:12:40.623
It's impossible to believe that even the English

00:12:40.823 --> 00:12:43.511
who were so difficult to even pronounce

00:12:43.712 --> 00:12:46.224
one sentence in Hindi language,

00:12:46.425 --> 00:12:50.424
are now fluently speaking Sanskrit and talking all these things;

00:12:50.684 --> 00:12:54.450
because of this creativity improves you.

00:12:54.673 --> 00:12:57.814
We have so many artists in India who came to Sahaja Yoga,

00:12:58.014 --> 00:12:59.924
I don’t know if you know their names or not

00:13:00.124 --> 00:13:03.214
like Amjad Ali, Jalota, so many of them.

00:13:03.414 --> 00:13:04.736
They got their Realization

00:13:04.937 --> 00:13:08.253
and after that, now today they are very well-known artists.

00:13:08.454 --> 00:13:11.944
Also the paintings: we have some Australian people,

00:13:12.144 --> 00:13:14.404
who became quite good artists,

00:13:14.604 --> 00:13:16.324
after coming to Sahaja Yoga.

00:13:16.524 --> 00:13:22.053
So it gives you a sense of aesthetics,

00:13:22.254 --> 00:13:26.204
and also it gives you the energy to express yourself.

00:13:26.494 --> 00:13:30.872
Now if you have the technique of how to create anything

00:13:31.073 --> 00:13:34.404
say you want to make a house or you want to paint,

00:13:34.605 --> 00:13:37.039
or if you want to do something,

00:13:37.240 --> 00:13:39.484
mouldings or anything that you want to do

00:13:39.684 --> 00:13:42.604
if you have the technique,

00:13:42.924 --> 00:13:46.404
the creativity, the power of creativity starts pouring in you,

00:13:46.604 --> 00:13:48.217
and you start producing things

00:13:48.418 --> 00:13:51.654
on which you cannot even have thought of,

00:13:51.854 --> 00:13:53.824
and these things happen to a person.

00:13:54.024 --> 00:13:57.423
So a person can become extremely dynamic with this.

00:13:57.645 --> 00:14:02.054
But if with that you do not keep your Sahaja Yoga practice,

00:14:02.254 --> 00:14:06.013
means if you do not keep your connection with the Divine,

00:14:06.214 --> 00:14:08.564
then the energy gets exhausted.

00:14:08.814 --> 00:14:11.364
That’s why Self-Realization is very important

00:14:11.564 --> 00:14:14.134
for every artist,

00:14:14.334 --> 00:14:16.884
that he should get his connection

00:14:17.084 --> 00:14:18.904
with this All-pervading Power

00:14:19.104 --> 00:14:21.644
which is the combination of all the powers,

00:14:21.844 --> 00:14:24.544
so that he doesn’t feel exhausted with it.

00:14:24.744 --> 00:14:29.019
Not only that, but all the time this source is flowing into him.

00:14:29.273 --> 00:14:32.624
Constantly it has to flow, and that’s why you have to do

00:14:32.824 --> 00:14:34.581
a little practice of Sahaja Yoga,

00:14:34.782 --> 00:14:37.394
after getting your Realization, as I told you yesterday,

00:14:37.594 --> 00:14:39.604
that now you don’t stop at this point,

00:14:39.804 --> 00:14:41.864
you have to make the connection perfect.

00:14:42.065 --> 00:14:44.587
Without the connection,

00:14:44.787 --> 00:14:47.643
it may be that you may go down.

00:14:47.844 --> 00:14:51.922
So it’s best is to keep your connection on and work it out,

00:14:52.123 --> 00:14:56.324
to give full respect to yourself,

00:14:56.570 --> 00:14:58.223
to your being.

00:14:58.424 --> 00:15:00.774
You are not an ordinary thing,

00:15:00.974 --> 00:15:03.234
you are not a chicken or something like that.

00:15:03.434 --> 00:15:04.853
You are a human being.

00:15:05.054 --> 00:15:08.214
And the beauty that is within you is to be discovered,

00:15:08.424 --> 00:15:09.947
is to be nourished

00:15:10.148 --> 00:15:12.564
and to be proud of.

00:15:12.764 --> 00:15:15.181
It is such a great thing you have within yourself,

00:15:15.382 --> 00:15:18.333
the powers, which I’ll tell you one by one.

00:15:18.534 --> 00:15:23.124
Now above that is the, you see the third center.

00:15:23.324 --> 00:15:26.418
which is called as Nabhi, means the navel.

00:15:26.794 --> 00:15:31.004
This is the center of

00:15:31.654 --> 00:15:35.764
the way we absorb the virtues,

00:15:36.334 --> 00:15:39.564
or the virtues are enlightened.

00:15:39.764 --> 00:15:41.974
When this center is enlightened

00:15:42.174 --> 00:15:43.774
we really become righteous.

00:15:43.974 --> 00:15:46.844
We don’t have to tell, “Now you don’t do this and don’t do that”.

00:15:47.044 --> 00:15:48.448
You just become.

00:15:48.649 --> 00:15:50.893
Like a saint, a real saint,

00:15:51.094 --> 00:15:53.284
will not do wrong things.

00:15:53.484 --> 00:15:57.093
In the same way when a person gets his Realization,

00:15:57.294 --> 00:15:59.554
by the virtue of this center,

00:15:59.754 --> 00:16:03.104
he becomes absolutely balanced:

00:16:04.224 --> 00:16:07.784
balanced with his family life, with his wife, with his children,

00:16:08.014 --> 00:16:10.654
balanced with the politics, economics,

00:16:10.854 --> 00:16:12.684
balanced with the society,

00:16:12.884 --> 00:16:16.094
balanced with all the people whom he knows;

00:16:16.294 --> 00:16:20.464
in a very balancing way he starts behaving.

00:16:20.664 --> 00:16:23.003
There’s not one-sided activity.

00:16:23.204 --> 00:16:26.647
For example, somebody may be very much attached to the wife

00:16:26.934 --> 00:16:29.104
and may try to harm others.

00:16:29.354 --> 00:16:32.211
Somebody who is very much attached to others,

00:16:32.411 --> 00:16:33.725
may harm his wife.

00:16:33.926 --> 00:16:37.144
So a kind of a balance is established by this,

00:16:37.374 --> 00:16:39.854
and a person who gets this

00:16:40.054 --> 00:16:43.613
develops a personality which we call as regal.

00:16:43.814 --> 00:16:46.654
That sense of dignity comes into such a person.

00:16:46.864 --> 00:16:50.313
Now you see our children have lost the virtues,

00:16:50.514 --> 00:16:52.884
our children don’t have that regalty.

00:16:53.084 --> 00:16:55.199
They have become very cheapish also,

00:16:55.399 --> 00:16:57.947
and they run after materialism and things like that;

00:16:58.148 --> 00:16:59.979
they fight for small, small things.

00:17:00.180 --> 00:17:03.044
It’s not only children, even the grown-ups are like that

00:17:03.244 --> 00:17:05.244
and they try to waste their energy,

00:17:05.444 --> 00:17:07.904
fighting for something that is so useless.

00:17:08.104 --> 00:17:11.028
So by enlightenment of this center

00:17:11.229 --> 00:17:14.744
you understand the value of matter.

00:17:15.024 --> 00:17:17.324
And the value of matter is this:

00:17:17.525 --> 00:17:19.724
that it has aesthetics, first of all,

00:17:19.924 --> 00:17:24.594
and secondly, you can express your love only through matter.

00:17:24.804 --> 00:17:27.724
If you love somebody you’ll give them something,

00:17:27.924 --> 00:17:30.724
a little flower also can express your love.

00:17:30.924 --> 00:17:33.684
Anything can express your love through matter,

00:17:33.884 --> 00:17:35.964
and then you become a very generous

00:17:36.164 --> 00:17:38.494
and very enjoyable person.

00:17:38.694 --> 00:17:40.171
Some people feel

00:17:40.372 --> 00:17:42.403
that if you become generous, you will be bankrupt.

00:17:42.604 --> 00:17:44.545
It’s not so. On the contrary,

00:17:44.746 --> 00:17:48.034
if you open one door, no air will come in,

00:17:48.264 --> 00:17:52.208
but if you open the other door, all the air will start circulating.

00:17:52.409 --> 00:17:55.574
In the same way, when a person is generous

00:17:55.774 --> 00:17:58.155
he starts getting so many blessings -

00:17:58.356 --> 00:18:01.836
because he is also connected with the Divine - that he is amazed.

00:18:02.037 --> 00:18:04.484
He doesn’t know what to do with the things that he has got,

00:18:04.684 --> 00:18:06.534
and then he starts pouring it to others.

00:18:06.734 --> 00:18:09.222
There are so many things people are telling Me about,

00:18:09.423 --> 00:18:12.235
miracles and miracles of even material things

00:18:12.435 --> 00:18:16.364
in their jobs, in their purchasing, in their shopping,

00:18:16.564 --> 00:18:19.204
the way they have seen miracles happening

00:18:19.404 --> 00:18:21.494
that it is nothing but just

00:18:21.694 --> 00:18:24.654
that this center is enlightened.

00:18:24.854 --> 00:18:29.164
And with this center, within you a righteousness comes in.

00:18:29.484 --> 00:18:33.513
And this righteousness doesn’t force anybody else,

00:18:33.714 --> 00:18:38.778
it’s just righteousness itself which doesn’t command anything

00:18:38.979 --> 00:18:40.571
or demand anything,

00:18:40.772 --> 00:18:43.769
but it becomes a respectable personality,

00:18:43.970 --> 00:18:47.214
and you just start really understanding

00:18:47.414 --> 00:18:48.603
that, “Look at this man”.

00:18:48.804 --> 00:18:51.736
Somebody was telling Me today that in the office people asked,

00:18:51.937 --> 00:18:54.204
“How are you so dignified?”

00:18:54.404 --> 00:18:56.224
He said, “I didn’t know I was so dignified.”

00:18:56.424 --> 00:18:58.424
"No, you don’t do anything undignified,

00:18:58.624 --> 00:19:01.924
and you do everything just like a child also".

00:19:02.124 --> 00:19:04.934
So there’s a child-like dignity you develop,

00:19:05.134 --> 00:19:08.484
and it’s a beautiful thing to happen, really it’s angelic.

00:19:08.704 --> 00:19:11.393
Now then there, we have another center on top,

00:19:11.594 --> 00:19:13.623
which we call as the heart center.

00:19:13.824 --> 00:19:15.854
It is in the center.

00:19:16.054 --> 00:19:18.223
Now in the sternum bone, behind the sternum bone

00:19:18.424 --> 00:19:19.704
this center is there,

00:19:19.905 --> 00:19:23.477
and thymus produces the antibodies

00:19:23.678 --> 00:19:25.243
in your sternum bone.

00:19:25.444 --> 00:19:29.115
These antibodies, later on, fight your diseases.

00:19:30.024 --> 00:19:32.003
When you are about twelve years of age

00:19:32.204 --> 00:19:34.662
they go into the whole body, and waiting there,

00:19:34.863 --> 00:19:40.770
for a signal from your sternum bone.

00:19:41.204 --> 00:19:43.682
That means supposing you see something, you get frightened,

00:19:43.883 --> 00:19:45.529
this bone starts pulsating.

00:19:45.730 --> 00:19:48.964
When it pulsates, the antibodies know there’s some emergency,

00:19:49.164 --> 00:19:51.203
and they get prepared for it.

00:19:51.404 --> 00:19:55.672
Now this is such a normal thing to happen to people.

00:19:55.873 --> 00:19:59.534
But the insecurities can be of the worst type,

00:19:59.734 --> 00:20:02.264
and when these insecurities develop,

00:20:02.464 --> 00:20:05.264
people can develop all kinds of diseases of the lungs;

00:20:05.464 --> 00:20:07.014
specially the women develop

00:20:07.214 --> 00:20:09.464
what you call as the breast cancer.

00:20:09.704 --> 00:20:11.294
Mostly these women are insecure:

00:20:11.494 --> 00:20:14.224
maybe their husbands are not good, or they feel

00:20:14.424 --> 00:20:17.214
that the husband may leave them alone or something like that.

00:20:17.414 --> 00:20:20.134
There are certain insecurities that are built in.

00:20:20.344 --> 00:20:23.244
They might be quite frightened people, personalities.

00:20:23.444 --> 00:20:25.443
I have seen most of the air-hostesses

00:20:25.644 --> 00:20:27.543
have this center heart catching,

00:20:27.744 --> 00:20:30.580
because they are afraid they may miss the plane or I don’t know,

00:20:30.781 --> 00:20:33.264
they have to be on the job and run and do.

00:20:33.464 --> 00:20:36.044
Mostly these time-bound jobs

00:20:36.244 --> 00:20:39.564
cause you a trouble here of the center heart,

00:20:39.824 --> 00:20:42.344
and this center heart is very important,

00:20:42.544 --> 00:20:45.244
because for women specially, they have to be secured.

00:20:45.464 --> 00:20:48.584
If their motherhood is challenged then they are even worse.

00:20:48.784 --> 00:20:50.888
And this is how one has to understand,

00:20:51.089 --> 00:20:53.334
a woman should be very much respected

00:20:53.534 --> 00:20:56.834
if she is your wife, she’s your child or anything.

00:20:57.035 --> 00:21:00.254
She has to be respected and given all the security.

00:21:00.454 --> 00:21:02.374
It’s the woman who makes the society,

00:21:02.574 --> 00:21:04.284
it's the woman who creates the children,

00:21:04.484 --> 00:21:06.603
it's the woman who looks after the children.

00:21:06.804 --> 00:21:10.533
So the men have to give all the security and the protection

00:21:10.734 --> 00:21:14.884
to the womenhood and understand that is a very important factor,

00:21:15.084 --> 00:21:19.564
which if we neglect we can have lots of problems with our society;

00:21:19.764 --> 00:21:22.144
and the women will start competing with men

00:21:22.344 --> 00:21:25.664
and then the society will be all dislocated.

00:21:26.924 --> 00:21:29.894
So the center on the left side and the right side

00:21:30.094 --> 00:21:34.044
are the centers of your father, of your mother and your father.

00:21:34.454 --> 00:21:36.374
If there’s any problem with your father,

00:21:36.574 --> 00:21:40.604
then the right side catches and it gives you asthma.

00:21:40.804 --> 00:21:43.058
First of all you are, we can say,

00:21:43.259 --> 00:21:45.244
vulnerable to asthma, due to bad liver.

00:21:45.444 --> 00:21:47.123
Plus if you have problems with your father

00:21:47.324 --> 00:21:48.944
or if with your fatherhood -

00:21:49.144 --> 00:21:50.864
supposing you are an unhappy father,

00:21:51.064 --> 00:21:53.774
or maybe that you are not looking after your children,

00:21:53.974 --> 00:21:56.544
then you get this center caught up very badly.

00:21:56.774 --> 00:21:58.659
Then on the left side is the mother’s,

00:21:58.860 --> 00:22:01.563
and the mother’s thing is that when some mothers

00:22:01.764 --> 00:22:04.581
are not good mothers; also children can get this.

00:22:04.782 --> 00:22:10.704
Or when the children are not nice to the mother, they also get it.

00:22:10.904 --> 00:22:15.224
So mother and father are very important factors in Sahaja Yoga,

00:22:15.424 --> 00:22:17.429
and you have to understand

00:22:17.630 --> 00:22:20.500
that if your parents have been unkind to you,

00:22:20.701 --> 00:22:22.979
you must forgive them. Just forget about them.

00:22:23.180 --> 00:22:25.642
Because they have given you birth, you should be thankful,

00:22:25.843 --> 00:22:27.334
and just forget about them.

00:22:27.534 --> 00:22:32.254
That’s the best way to get over the problem of left and right heart.

00:22:32.704 --> 00:22:35.764
Then we have, on top, if you see, is this chakra

00:22:35.964 --> 00:22:38.943
which we call as the Vishuddhi chakra.

00:22:39.144 --> 00:22:42.224
This Vishuddhi chakra is, has got sixteen petals,

00:22:42.424 --> 00:22:46.644
and looks after our ear, nose, eyes, throat, everything.

00:22:46.884 --> 00:22:51.174
Our face, everything is looked after by this center.

00:22:51.424 --> 00:22:53.264
Now this center also has left and right.

00:22:53.464 --> 00:22:54.974
All centers have left and right

00:22:55.174 --> 00:22:57.454
and when you feel guilty

00:22:57.654 --> 00:23:00.064
the left center catches,

00:23:00.264 --> 00:23:01.880
which is a very dangerous thing

00:23:02.081 --> 00:23:04.854
because this gives you diseases like angina,

00:23:05.054 --> 00:23:10.093
or maybe diseases like spondylitis and lethargic organs.

00:23:10.294 --> 00:23:13.844
Right when a person is very aggressive, talks very aggressively,

00:23:14.054 --> 00:23:16.534
and tries to dominate others,

00:23:16.734 --> 00:23:21.639
and use his power of speech to show off,

00:23:21.840 --> 00:23:23.240
the right side catches.

00:23:23.441 --> 00:23:27.224
The reactions of this can be many, that the hands gets frozen,

00:23:27.424 --> 00:23:30.384
and they also get the cancer of the throat;

00:23:30.584 --> 00:23:32.244
all kinds of things can happen

00:23:32.444 --> 00:23:35.604
with this chakra being in trouble.

00:23:35.994 --> 00:23:40.524
Now then we go to the chakra here, in between the optic chiasma.

00:23:40.724 --> 00:23:43.494
It is placed like this, and it’s absolutely closed.

00:23:43.694 --> 00:23:45.549
It is when you forgive.

00:23:45.750 --> 00:23:48.178
Christ has said that you have to forgive.

00:23:48.378 --> 00:23:50.953
When you forgive

00:23:51.154 --> 00:23:54.348
everyone and also when

00:23:55.364 --> 00:23:58.324
you ask for forgiveness,

00:23:58.984 --> 00:24:01.084
this chakra opens like this.

00:24:01.334 --> 00:24:02.917
Otherwise it cannot open.

00:24:03.117 --> 00:24:05.296
We saw yesterday that some people,

00:24:05.497 --> 00:24:07.924
at least there were ten, fifteen people

00:24:08.124 --> 00:24:10.894
who never got their Realization, because they had not forgiven.

00:24:11.094 --> 00:24:13.854
Then when I put My hand, worked on them and it worked.

00:24:14.054 --> 00:24:16.144
But it’s very simple to forgive,

00:24:16.344 --> 00:24:18.144
because whether you forgive or don’t forgive,

00:24:18.344 --> 00:24:19.897
you don’t do anything, it’s a myth,

00:24:20.098 --> 00:24:22.252
it’s absolutely a myth that you don’t forgive.

00:24:22.453 --> 00:24:25.414
But for that myth you suffered so much.

00:24:25.644 --> 00:24:29.174
So you have to forgive, to open this center of Agnya.

00:24:29.374 --> 00:24:31.854
It’s very important and is,

00:24:32.054 --> 00:24:34.894
the deity on that is Jesus Christ.

00:24:35.114 --> 00:24:37.764
Then you enter into the area called limbic area

00:24:37.964 --> 00:24:40.824
which is on top, which is called as Sahasrara in Sanskrit,

00:24:41.024 --> 00:24:43.772
means there are one thousand petals.

00:24:44.074 --> 00:24:47.044
These look like

00:24:47.564 --> 00:24:49.904
“tongues of flames” as described in the Bible.

00:24:50.104 --> 00:24:52.024
All of them look like “tongues of flames”

00:24:52.224 --> 00:24:55.853
but in the brain they are of seven colors,

00:24:56.054 --> 00:25:01.080
beautifully, very silently, peacefully

00:25:02.701 --> 00:25:05.413
opening, closing, opening, closing.

00:25:05.614 --> 00:25:08.524
So when the Kundalini goes into the limbic area

00:25:08.724 --> 00:25:11.450
it enlightens your brain, it enlightens.

00:25:11.651 --> 00:25:13.974
And as I told yesterday there are many children

00:25:14.174 --> 00:25:16.590
who have been dullards, have now

00:25:16.791 --> 00:25:19.401
records in their examination,

00:25:19.602 --> 00:25:22.280
and they have put so much of

00:25:22.480 --> 00:25:25.223
new dimension to their understanding,

00:25:25.424 --> 00:25:28.704
that their teachers, their professors are surprised.

00:25:28.904 --> 00:25:31.504
This is what happens when the brain,

00:25:31.704 --> 00:25:34.524
which is used very little, starts getting enlightened.

00:25:34.724 --> 00:25:37.293
Automatically you start using it.

00:25:37.494 --> 00:25:40.204
Then it pierces through the fontanel bone area,

00:25:40.404 --> 00:25:42.664
which is a very soft bone,

00:25:43.284 --> 00:25:46.193
through which this Kundalini comes out.

00:25:46.394 --> 00:25:52.183
I told you yesterday that Kundalini is your mother,

00:25:52.384 --> 00:25:53.704
individual mother,

00:25:53.904 --> 00:25:57.494
and she is the power of pure desire.

00:25:57.724 --> 00:26:00.844
All other desires that we have are impure.

00:26:01.044 --> 00:26:05.500
Today we want to have, say, a chair,

00:26:05.700 --> 00:26:08.963
then we want to have a table, then we want to have a house, then...

00:26:09.164 --> 00:26:11.630
We are never satisfied, we go from one to another;

00:26:11.837 --> 00:26:16.933
and it is a principle of economics that

00:26:17.134 --> 00:26:20.134
wants are not satiable in general.

00:26:20.334 --> 00:26:22.704
So what is that want which is satiable?

00:26:22.904 --> 00:26:24.804
Is this want, this pure desire.

00:26:25.004 --> 00:26:26.351
And what is the pure desire,

00:26:26.551 --> 00:26:29.063
is to be one with this divine power.

00:26:29.264 --> 00:26:30.744
Whether you know it or not,

00:26:30.944 --> 00:26:32.653
whether you are aware of it or not,

00:26:32.854 --> 00:26:34.944
it exists in all the human beings

00:26:35.144 --> 00:26:37.284
and the only thing that has to be done is

00:26:37.484 --> 00:26:39.614
it is to be awakened

00:26:39.814 --> 00:26:42.933
and to be connected to this All-pervading Power.

00:26:43.133 --> 00:26:44.787
So the truth is that

00:26:44.987 --> 00:26:48.639
you are not this body, not this mind,

00:26:48.840 --> 00:26:51.803
not these conditionings or ego,

00:26:52.004 --> 00:26:54.063
but you are the pure Spirit.

00:26:54.264 --> 00:26:59.054
And the second one, is that with this All-pervading Power,

00:26:59.254 --> 00:27:01.164
which is a wonderful thing,

00:27:01.364 --> 00:27:04.854
is impossible to describe it in this short lecture of Mine

00:27:05.054 --> 00:27:07.963
but it’s the one which organizes,

00:27:08.164 --> 00:27:10.134
which does all the living work.

00:27:10.334 --> 00:27:12.684
To the minutest things it organizes,

00:27:12.884 --> 00:27:15.272
so complicated everything is,

00:27:15.472 --> 00:27:17.130
but it manages all that.

00:27:17.331 --> 00:27:19.666
Not only, but above all,

00:27:19.867 --> 00:27:22.453
it forgives and it loves.

00:27:22.654 --> 00:27:25.344
So such a beautiful power is all around us,

00:27:25.544 --> 00:27:27.394
so why should we have any worry?

00:27:27.594 --> 00:27:30.424
And now we have to know

00:27:30.624 --> 00:27:32.497
that yesterday we had lots of questions,

00:27:32.698 --> 00:27:34.164
and nice questions were there.

00:27:34.364 --> 00:27:37.024
Today also I would like you to ask Me questions.

00:27:37.224 --> 00:27:39.602
But in asking questions, please remember

00:27:39.803 --> 00:27:42.681
not to ask “What is Your opinion about this person or that person?”

00:27:42.882 --> 00:27:45.605
Of course, now you must have known that I condemn all the people

00:27:45.806 --> 00:27:48.574
who take money in the name of God; absolutely openly.

00:27:48.774 --> 00:27:51.605
So please don’t ask Me questions about such people.

00:27:51.806 --> 00:27:56.084
Moreover, you ask questions which are related to our subject,

00:27:56.284 --> 00:27:57.904
because I have come here

00:27:58.104 --> 00:27:59.694
not to get anything out of you,

00:27:59.894 --> 00:28:01.734
but to give you what is your own:

00:28:01.934 --> 00:28:04.884
your beauty, your divinity, your glory.

00:28:05.084 --> 00:28:07.425
And then you will be surprised

00:28:07.626 --> 00:28:10.963
that the first thing that happens to you

00:28:11.163 --> 00:28:13.540
is a new awareness, it's a new dimension

00:28:13.740 --> 00:28:16.303
in your awareness comes in

00:28:16.504 --> 00:28:20.334
and this awareness is called as collective consciousness,

00:28:20.534 --> 00:28:23.054
by which you feel others on your fingertips.

00:28:23.254 --> 00:28:25.544
Who is the other then?

00:28:26.308 --> 00:28:30.893
Also within yourself you can feel what’s wrong with you.

00:28:31.094 --> 00:28:34.634
Only thing, you have to be decoding these signals

00:28:34.844 --> 00:28:37.332
and you should know how to correct it.

00:28:37.533 --> 00:28:40.414
This is what has to happen, which is very simple.

00:28:40.614 --> 00:28:43.334
Within a month’s time you can become your own masters,

00:28:43.534 --> 00:28:47.484
and you know how to treat yourself and how to look after yourself.

00:28:47.974 --> 00:28:50.424
I’m sorry I am here in only for today.

00:28:50.624 --> 00:28:52.254
Tomorrow I have to go to Canberra.

00:28:52.454 --> 00:28:54.704
And in this lecture,

00:28:54.904 --> 00:28:57.414
whatever was possible in short, I've tried to tell you

00:28:57.614 --> 00:29:00.414
about this great mechanism that is within us.

00:29:00.615 --> 00:29:04.083
But by this you achieve so many beautiful things,

00:29:04.284 --> 00:29:05.787
as I told you yesterday,

00:29:05.988 --> 00:29:08.993
that you achieve the peace,

00:29:09.194 --> 00:29:11.175
you achieve the witness state,

00:29:11.384 --> 00:29:13.734
you achieve the collective consciousness,

00:29:13.935 --> 00:29:15.936
you achieve

00:29:16.270 --> 00:29:21.943
the light in your attention, which acts.

00:29:22.144 --> 00:29:26.598
You pay attention to something, it acts, it works.

00:29:26.854 --> 00:29:30.444
Then you get the power that you can raise the Kundalini of others.

00:29:30.644 --> 00:29:34.493
Like one light enlightened can enlighten another light.

00:29:34.694 --> 00:29:38.004
Then it gives you a complete idea

00:29:38.244 --> 00:29:41.502
about yourself and about others.

00:29:41.924 --> 00:29:46.031
Above all, you get an absolute knowledge

00:29:46.404 --> 00:29:48.014
about everything.

00:29:48.224 --> 00:29:51.440
When you have the absolute knowledge, there’s no quarrel, no war,

00:29:51.641 --> 00:29:55.693
because everybody knows it on their fingertips.

00:29:55.894 --> 00:30:00.004
To know on your central nervous system is the real bodha,

00:30:00.204 --> 00:30:02.267
from where the word Buddha has come,

00:30:02.468 --> 00:30:05.183
is the "vida", from where the word Vedas has come.

00:30:05.384 --> 00:30:09.384
Gnostics, “gn”: “gn” means “jnana”. “Jnana” means the knowledge.

00:30:09.604 --> 00:30:11.879
And the knowledge is not mental knowledge,

00:30:12.080 --> 00:30:15.334
but the knowledge on your central nervous system.

00:30:15.534 --> 00:30:20.744
Whatever we have achieved in our ascent as human beings,

00:30:20.944 --> 00:30:24.304
we have got all this on our central nervous system.

00:30:24.504 --> 00:30:30.253
For example, you take a dog or a horse through a dirty place,

00:30:30.454 --> 00:30:32.032
he can pass through easily;

00:30:32.233 --> 00:30:33.758
but a human being cannot pass,

00:30:33.959 --> 00:30:37.053
because he has developed a new awareness about it.

00:30:37.254 --> 00:30:40.763
He knows what is beauty is, he knows what virtues are,

00:30:40.964 --> 00:30:42.993
he knows what is sin is.

00:30:43.194 --> 00:30:45.814
For an animal there is no sin, he’ll do whatever he likes,

00:30:46.014 --> 00:30:50.160
because he’s completely under the control of the Divine.

00:30:50.513 --> 00:30:52.963
But for human beings there’s freedom,

00:30:53.164 --> 00:30:56.804
and he has to judge it with trial and error

00:30:57.004 --> 00:30:58.994
and reach a point to understand

00:30:59.194 --> 00:31:03.944
that he has to get to a higher awareness.

00:31:04.654 --> 00:31:06.951
May God bless you all.

00:31:24.715 --> 00:31:27.109
Thank you.

00:31:36.704 --> 00:31:41.656
You have to ask the questions. I think they are all forgotten!

00:31:59.094 --> 00:32:01.909
Are melanomas and skin-cancers

00:32:02.110 --> 00:32:04.464
caused by a blockage in a chakra?

00:32:04.704 --> 00:32:07.607
Yes, all. Of course,

00:32:07.808 --> 00:32:10.509
all our diseases are because of the blockage in the chakras,

00:32:10.710 --> 00:32:11.733
no doubt.

00:32:11.934 --> 00:32:15.294
But see now, if you have to treat a tree

00:32:15.494 --> 00:32:18.484
and you start putting the medicine on the leaves,

00:32:18.684 --> 00:32:21.334
it will never be cured. You have to go to the roots.

00:32:21.534 --> 00:32:24.024
And because it is at the roots, it’s so simple.

00:32:24.224 --> 00:32:27.989
Only there are seven chakras and three nadis

00:32:28.190 --> 00:32:31.131
means about twenty-one permutations and combinations,

00:32:31.332 --> 00:32:33.808
you have to work out, that’s all.

00:32:49.316 --> 00:32:54.912
In meditation, where should we put our consciousness in the body?

00:32:55.924 --> 00:32:58.884
You don’t have to do anything, you just get into it.

00:32:59.084 --> 00:33:01.964
When the Kundalini crosses over this center,

00:33:02.164 --> 00:33:04.324
immediately you become thoughtlessly aware.

00:33:04.564 --> 00:33:06.974
That’s a state when you are in the present,

00:33:07.174 --> 00:33:09.464
neither in the future, not in the past.

00:33:09.694 --> 00:33:13.683
and then the growth, spiritual growth starts working it out.

00:33:13.884 --> 00:33:15.703
And suddenly you will find one day

00:33:15.904 --> 00:33:20.981
that you have touched that depth of your divinity.

00:33:24.624 --> 00:33:26.624
You don’t have to direct yourself at all.

00:33:26.824 --> 00:33:29.224
The Kundalini itself directs.

00:33:44.717 --> 00:33:46.294
Yes?

00:33:46.494 --> 00:33:49.692
Mother, I'd like to know the relationship

00:33:49.893 --> 00:33:53.297
between what is happening in the world in terms of the pollution

00:33:53.498 --> 00:33:56.717
and the damage that's been [unclear] and harms us

00:33:56.918 --> 00:33:59.745
Is there an object, a lesson for mankind in that?

00:33:59.946 --> 00:34:02.249
And I suppose, most, most of us would say "yes",

00:34:02.450 --> 00:34:05.195
but what is the spiritual aspect of what we are doing to our world,

00:34:05.396 --> 00:34:06.728
[what is spiritually to be done]?

00:34:06.929 --> 00:34:10.817
- What's this?
What is the spiritual significance

00:34:11.018 --> 00:34:14.893
on what we are doing to our world in the sense of pollution?

00:34:15.094 --> 00:34:19.692
Yes, spiritual aspect is that we do not have a balance.

00:34:21.974 --> 00:34:25.053
Now once we start a machine,

00:34:25.254 --> 00:34:28.613
then machine has to produce, go on producing like mad.

00:34:28.883 --> 00:34:30.763
It produces more and more.

00:34:30.964 --> 00:34:34.173
Then the accent is on money, not on Spirit.

00:34:34.374 --> 00:34:35.757
So what happens?

00:34:35.958 --> 00:34:38.414
That they produce more and more things

00:34:38.614 --> 00:34:42.734
and they create an atmosphere through advertisement, this, that

00:34:42.974 --> 00:34:46.223
and everybody starts running for it.

00:34:46.424 --> 00:34:50.904
Then we have accumulation of so much of rubbish,

00:34:51.104 --> 00:34:54.933
and what you have done is that you have exhausted the Mother Earth.

00:34:55.134 --> 00:34:58.724
But when you get your Realization and when you are spiritual,

00:34:58.924 --> 00:35:01.574
then what happens, you buy very few things,

00:35:01.774 --> 00:35:03.573
but very good things.

00:35:03.774 --> 00:35:06.422
You don’t run after the fashions or anything,

00:35:06.622 --> 00:35:08.573
but you make a dress

00:35:08.774 --> 00:35:12.044
which is good for you, which is decent for you,

00:35:12.264 --> 00:35:16.444
and may not be one hundred dresses,

00:35:16.644 --> 00:35:18.644
maybe five or six,

00:35:18.844 --> 00:35:23.573
but very beautiful, dignified, artistic dresses.

00:35:23.774 --> 00:35:26.535
In the same way now, supposing

00:35:27.124 --> 00:35:29.984
I tell you that “you don’t drink any alcohol,”

00:35:30.184 --> 00:35:32.823
you will all run away. But I don’t say that.

00:35:33.024 --> 00:35:36.024
After Sahaja Yoga, people just don’t drink.

00:35:36.304 --> 00:35:38.094
Now your money is saved by that.

00:35:38.294 --> 00:35:40.865
But also what is saved in that is

00:35:41.065 --> 00:35:46.784
the amount of paraphernalia you need for a drinking party!

00:35:50.984 --> 00:35:55.087
First time, in India I never used to serve any drinks in My house,

00:35:55.288 --> 00:35:57.505
but C.P. said, "In England You have to do it”.

00:35:57.706 --> 00:35:59.499
My husband said,“You have to do it there” .

00:35:59.700 --> 00:36:01.654
I said, “All right, that’s your lookout, not Mine”.

00:36:01.884 --> 00:36:04.425
So he got hold of a dictionary, you see,

00:36:04.626 --> 00:36:06.092
a French dictionary, to find out

00:36:06.293 --> 00:36:08.783
what all we have to buy to begin with.

00:36:08.984 --> 00:36:11.538
So you’ll be amazed, at that time -

00:36:11.739 --> 00:36:16.466
it was in 1973 we went to London, yes -

00:36:16.667 --> 00:36:18.230
and he said that,

00:36:18.430 --> 00:36:22.882
“At least we’ll have to pay nine hundred pounds,

00:36:23.134 --> 00:36:25.694
to get the best quality tumblers”.

00:36:25.894 --> 00:36:28.713
I said, “Nine hundred pounds for what?” He said,

00:36:28.914 --> 00:36:32.703
“For everything you have to have a different type of a tumbler.”

00:36:32.904 --> 00:36:35.854
I said, “Really, but for what? What is the need?”

00:36:36.054 --> 00:36:38.794
He said, “That’s the custom, that’s the norm”.

00:36:38.994 --> 00:36:41.524
So you see, also the norms that we have created

00:36:41.724 --> 00:36:44.431
are so stupid. There is no need.

00:36:44.864 --> 00:36:47.504
Instead of that in India supposing you are well off, all right,

00:36:47.704 --> 00:36:52.683
they’ll have six tumblers made of silver,

00:36:52.884 --> 00:36:56.484
which they’ll pass on from father to son,

00:36:56.734 --> 00:37:00.224
son to his son, and that’s all.

00:37:01.064 --> 00:37:02.654
You won’t need many things.

00:37:02.854 --> 00:37:07.166
Or plates now; so you’ll have first course, then a second course,

00:37:07.367 --> 00:37:10.243
and a third course, and then you start moving

00:37:10.444 --> 00:37:14.544
with all your cutlery this way, then this way, then this way,

00:37:14.744 --> 00:37:17.830
and really you don’t know what to do with it.

00:37:18.031 --> 00:37:19.713
So there’s no need to do all that.

00:37:19.914 --> 00:37:22.194
There’s no need, you see, to do it.

00:37:22.394 --> 00:37:24.083
What is the necessity, you see?

00:37:24.284 --> 00:37:27.701


00:37:27.902 --> 00:37:30.802
because after Realization you have vibrations in your hands,

00:37:31.003 --> 00:37:32.253
divine vibrations.

00:37:32.454 --> 00:37:34.115
So you start using your hands,

00:37:34.316 --> 00:37:38.574
and you can use a one nice plate of brass

00:37:38.774 --> 00:37:41.284
or of silver, in that same amount.

00:37:41.484 --> 00:37:43.764
You see, six plates of silver

00:37:43.964 --> 00:37:50.783
cost you the same as this elaborate, say, a dinner-set

00:37:50.984 --> 00:37:55.743
which is always, I would say,

00:37:55.944 --> 00:37:59.284
has to be replaced because it breaks, this happens, that happens.

00:37:59.484 --> 00:38:02.964
And the same plates you can pass on to other people.

00:38:03.165 --> 00:38:05.464
There are so many things, we waste our time.

00:38:05.664 --> 00:38:09.734
Now if you go to a lady’s apartment,

00:38:09.934 --> 00:38:12.674
you will be surprised that the whole place will be filled

00:38:12.874 --> 00:38:16.025
with this Elizabeth Arden, this, that, that, that.

00:38:16.226 --> 00:38:19.133
You open something, it all falls on you.

00:38:19.334 --> 00:38:21.357
And then you say, “Why have you got so many?”

00:38:21.558 --> 00:38:23.307
“No, Mother, this is gone out of fashion.”

00:38:23.508 --> 00:38:25.964
“Baba, whatever it was good for your skin,

00:38:26.184 --> 00:38:29.044
whatever was once good for you, use that throughout”.

00:38:29.244 --> 00:38:30.844
“No, but they are changing every time.”

00:38:31.044 --> 00:38:33.684
I said, “But you decide what you want to use it,

00:38:33.884 --> 00:38:36.184
and use that thing all through.

00:38:36.384 --> 00:38:39.644
What’s the use of filling these cupboards with all this?”

00:38:40.164 --> 00:38:43.369
You see, we were in London, we were searching out houses

00:38:43.570 --> 00:38:47.444
and I mean, horrible, I tell you, the experiences were.

00:38:47.724 --> 00:38:50.144
You go into any house and suddenly you’ll find

00:38:50.344 --> 00:38:52.364
two legs of the pants falling on, to your [room].

00:38:52.564 --> 00:38:55.148
And then you look up and there’s a pile of things

00:38:55.349 --> 00:38:56.764
kept on the top of the loft.

00:38:56.964 --> 00:38:59.364
Just the loft is overfilled with all the clothes.

00:38:59.564 --> 00:39:02.363
And so much was filled.

00:39:02.564 --> 00:39:05.564
I tell you, Australians are much more neater people,

00:39:05.765 --> 00:39:07.744
but if you go to England you’ll be shocked,

00:39:07.944 --> 00:39:10.167
because they are the buyers,

00:39:10.368 --> 00:39:13.254
for ages they have been buying, buying, buying, buying,

00:39:13.454 --> 00:39:15.684
and there’s no place for human beings to live inside.

00:39:15.885 --> 00:39:18.458
They live outside,

00:39:21.084 --> 00:39:22.315
in the Hyde Park!

00:39:22.516 --> 00:39:24.629
They are sitting in the Hyde Park. If you ask them,

00:39:24.830 --> 00:39:28.537
“Why are you here?”, “Our house are overfull”.

00:39:32.474 --> 00:39:34.124
So you develop the balance.

00:39:34.324 --> 00:39:36.613
And because of this lack of balance,

00:39:36.813 --> 00:39:39.669
there is ecological problem.

00:39:43.970 --> 00:39:45.607
Is Kundalini to be developed

00:39:45.807 --> 00:39:49.509
within certain age of human existence

00:39:49.710 --> 00:39:53.614
or can it be developed any age?

00:39:56.144 --> 00:39:59.852
Is the Kundalini to be developed

00:40:00.123 --> 00:40:03.659
you know, at a certain age in human existence,

00:40:03.860 --> 00:40:05.784
or can it be developed at any age?

00:40:06.024 --> 00:40:08.643
At any age. There’s nothing like that.

00:40:08.844 --> 00:40:13.481
There’s no age, no time, nothing. It’s beyond all that.

00:40:14.884 --> 00:40:17.824
Even so many children are born realized these days.

00:40:18.024 --> 00:40:21.374
Sahaja Yogis get the children, when they marry,

00:40:21.574 --> 00:40:23.814
they get children who are already born realized.

00:40:24.014 --> 00:40:26.653
They are so wise, you know, very wise,

00:40:26.854 --> 00:40:31.334
and they come and have a conference with Me very special.

00:40:31.534 --> 00:40:34.437
And then they tell Me about all the uncle and aunties,

00:40:34.638 --> 00:40:37.444
what’s wrong with their chakras.

00:40:40.573 --> 00:40:42.583
They are My great friends, I should say;

00:40:42.784 --> 00:40:45.485
but very wise, you know.

00:41:08.604 --> 00:41:11.614
She was recently told that she should never meditate

00:41:11.815 --> 00:41:14.184
unless she’s had a glass of water.

00:41:14.384 --> 00:41:16.418
- Should I? For Me?
- This is neccessary...

00:41:16.619 --> 00:41:19.573
- For Me?
- No, no, anyone meditating.

00:41:19.781 --> 00:41:22.908
- I didn’t understand, what is it?
- Nor did I.

00:41:24.248 --> 00:41:28.684
She said she was recently told that she shouldn’t meditate

00:41:28.885 --> 00:41:31.934
until she’s had a glass of water.

00:41:32.824 --> 00:41:35.596
Are you? Sahaja Yogis told you that?

00:41:35.796 --> 00:41:37.933
Yes, [finding how]...

00:41:38.134 --> 00:41:41.683
See, sometimes what happens, supposing you are a liver patient,

00:41:41.884 --> 00:41:45.574
then the heat might be generated out of your head, you see,

00:41:45.774 --> 00:41:47.583
like a chimney it opens out.

00:41:47.784 --> 00:41:49.428
So if you take little water,

00:41:49.629 --> 00:41:52.304
the heat won’t feel so much. May be that.

00:41:52.504 --> 00:41:54.614
But I get the heat from all the rest of the people,

00:41:54.822 --> 00:41:58.819
and I go on drinking water all the time to cool Myself, too.

00:42:09.511 --> 00:42:12.684
There are so many different forms of meditation.

00:42:12.884 --> 00:42:15.204
Does any sort of meditation work?

00:42:15.404 --> 00:42:18.623
No, no, it does not. We do not meditate,

00:42:18.824 --> 00:42:20.829
we have to be in meditation.

00:42:21.030 --> 00:42:23.333
There’s difference between the two.

00:42:23.534 --> 00:42:26.224
You do not meditate before Realization;

00:42:26.424 --> 00:42:29.863
after Realization you are in meditation.

00:42:30.064 --> 00:42:32.364
So you become thoughtlessly aware.

00:42:32.564 --> 00:42:34.814
So when you meditate in Sahaja Yoga

00:42:35.014 --> 00:42:37.334
you become thoughtlessly aware,

00:42:37.534 --> 00:42:41.824
and then you start growing into a new awareness

00:42:42.024 --> 00:42:43.284
or a higher awareness

00:42:43.484 --> 00:42:46.403
which you call as doubtless awareness,

00:42:46.604 --> 00:42:48.744
and that is how you start growing.

00:42:48.944 --> 00:42:52.774
So the meditation is that you get into meditation,

00:42:52.974 --> 00:42:55.404
you don’t do meditation.

00:42:56.824 --> 00:42:58.263
This one.

00:42:58.464 --> 00:43:01.479
If you are one of these people that are thinking all the time

00:43:01.680 --> 00:43:03.712
and you are blocking up the other side,

00:43:03.913 --> 00:43:06.573
how do you balance [that]?

00:43:06.774 --> 00:43:11.374
If you are an excessive thinker, if you’re thinking all the time,

00:43:11.574 --> 00:43:14.124
and this causes a block on the opposite side,

00:43:14.324 --> 00:43:16.974
how are you balance things out?

00:43:18.234 --> 00:43:22.863
Just by, you see, turning your hand left to the right.

00:43:23.064 --> 00:43:25.103
It's very simple.

00:43:25.304 --> 00:43:28.804
You won’t believe, but that’s how we manage it.

00:43:33.844 --> 00:43:36.281
First the vibrations must flow from your hand,

00:43:36.482 --> 00:43:38.084
then you will know how to balance.

00:43:38.284 --> 00:43:40.324
But when that doesn’t happen,

00:43:40.524 --> 00:43:44.064
then you can ask somebody to balance you.

00:44:18.964 --> 00:44:21.933
It’s quite a big question.

00:44:23.596 --> 00:44:30.509
He says, You appear to be forming a hypothesis about Kundalini

00:44:30.710 --> 00:44:34.903
and relating it to medical conditions.

00:44:35.104 --> 00:44:37.793
From where does this hypothesis come?

00:44:37.994 --> 00:44:40.664
- Hypothesis?
- About Kundalini.

00:44:40.954 --> 00:44:43.333
Is My own knowledge.

00:44:43.534 --> 00:44:47.929
I have also done medicine, to relate it to that.

00:44:49.814 --> 00:44:51.654
Is My own knowledge, I should say,

00:44:51.864 --> 00:44:54.254
and so many saints had this knowledge too.

00:44:54.454 --> 00:44:57.374
But the only thing I have done is I have related

00:44:57.574 --> 00:45:00.763
to not only to medical, but also to science.

00:45:00.964 --> 00:45:03.524
That’s very important. Apart from that,

00:45:03.724 --> 00:45:07.013
I have devised a method, I would say,

00:45:07.214 --> 00:45:10.882
of permutations and combinations of human problems.

00:45:11.664 --> 00:45:14.534
I’ve studied them and worked it out in such a way

00:45:14.734 --> 00:45:17.884
that en masse Realization can be given.

00:45:19.134 --> 00:45:23.884
You see, I always try not to talk about Myself

00:45:24.085 --> 00:45:27.613
because, you see, Christ said that He was the Son of God

00:45:27.814 --> 00:45:32.034
which was the truth, truth, absolute truth,

00:45:32.235 --> 00:45:34.423
but people crucified Him for that.

00:45:34.624 --> 00:45:37.544
Because people don’t understand divine things,

00:45:37.754 --> 00:45:39.533
they don’t understand, you see;

00:45:39.734 --> 00:45:41.894
they have no idea as to the divine Power,

00:45:42.094 --> 00:45:43.377
what it can do.

00:45:43.578 --> 00:45:45.254
So they don’t understand,

00:45:45.454 --> 00:45:47.814
so no use telling them about yourself.

00:45:48.054 --> 00:45:50.654
As I told you, that I want to live,

00:45:50.854 --> 00:45:54.440
I don’t want to get crucified just now.

00:46:17.442 --> 00:46:19.201
So when you are meditating

00:46:19.402 --> 00:46:21.373
and you feel a force within you blooming,

00:46:21.574 --> 00:46:24.243
could You explain what this force is?

00:46:24.444 --> 00:46:26.574
- When you are meditating?
- Yes.

00:46:26.774 --> 00:46:30.358
Now which meditation she is doing, first of all, let’s know.

00:46:30.558 --> 00:46:33.777
- What kind of meditation are you doing?

00:46:34.126 --> 00:46:35.603
Chanting meditation.

00:46:35.804 --> 00:46:37.684
Chanting?

00:46:38.168 --> 00:46:42.704
Chanting is absolutely wrong. Absolutely wrong.

00:46:43.263 --> 00:46:45.984
Because if you are not connected,

00:46:46.184 --> 00:46:50.213
supposing you are taking the name of God, any way,

00:46:50.414 --> 00:46:53.163
and you are not connected,

00:46:53.364 --> 00:46:56.064
then what’s the use of taking the name?

00:46:56.264 --> 00:47:00.403
You are not connected. It’s like telephoning without connection.

00:47:00.604 --> 00:47:02.188
It’s very practical.

00:47:02.389 --> 00:47:05.924
Moreover, say, if you have to meet,

00:47:06.124 --> 00:47:07.534
say, the Queen of England,

00:47:07.734 --> 00:47:09.623
you have to have a protocol.

00:47:09.824 --> 00:47:12.904
You have to know her, you have to go by proper channel.

00:47:13.104 --> 00:47:15.941
You cannot just go and say, “Oh, Elizabeth, Elizabeth, Elizabeth”.

00:47:16.142 --> 00:47:17.863
They’ll all arrest you there.

00:47:18.064 --> 00:47:20.643
And if you do chanting, then you get into troubles,

00:47:20.844 --> 00:47:22.623
terrible trouble.

00:47:22.824 --> 00:47:24.894
So you must have authority.

00:47:25.094 --> 00:47:26.733
God is not in your pocket,

00:47:26.934 --> 00:47:28.944
that you go on chanting His name all the time.

00:47:29.161 --> 00:47:32.099
But what you have to do is to

00:47:32.300 --> 00:47:34.484
be in His Kingdom;

00:47:34.694 --> 00:47:37.333
then even once if you take His name,

00:47:37.534 --> 00:47:40.109
you are blessed.

00:47:42.414 --> 00:47:46.934
Chanting is the most maddening thing, I think.

00:47:52.296 --> 00:47:56.486
There are a number of teachers, such as You say;

00:47:57.549 --> 00:48:03.359
they arrived to connect people to Divinity.

00:48:03.560 --> 00:48:06.309
On [unclear] born this divine time,

00:48:06.510 --> 00:48:09.162
what, how and what that relationship is

00:48:09.369 --> 00:48:13.352
between the teacher and those who do receive the connection?

00:48:13.553 --> 00:48:16.293
And whether it can be

00:48:16.494 --> 00:48:18.520
whether it needs to be just one teacher

00:48:18.720 --> 00:48:21.529
or whether a number of teachers to be?

00:48:22.579 --> 00:48:25.453
Just stand before the light, I can't see.

00:48:25.784 --> 00:48:28.974
There is a number, he says there are a number of teachers

00:48:29.174 --> 00:48:32.684
who can make this connection for one with the Divinity.

00:48:32.964 --> 00:48:35.824
I have not known any, so far.

00:48:36.024 --> 00:48:37.574
I have not known any.

00:48:37.774 --> 00:48:41.244
They are all in the market and making money, that’s all.

00:48:41.444 --> 00:48:43.949
I would like to know if there’s somebody else.

00:48:44.150 --> 00:48:46.889
But once you get your Realization,

00:48:47.090 --> 00:48:49.563
once you become a Sahaja Yogi,

00:48:49.764 --> 00:48:53.493
then you can give Realization to others. That’s different.

00:48:53.694 --> 00:48:57.484
But I have not known anyone so far who is doing this.

00:48:57.684 --> 00:49:00.882
If you know anyone, please let me know.

00:49:02.930 --> 00:49:05.794
What you see God as a [change]?

00:49:06.787 --> 00:49:07.887
Please translate.

00:49:08.088 --> 00:49:12.419
How do you see God, how do you describe God?

00:49:12.684 --> 00:49:15.404
Should I describe Him just now?

00:49:16.734 --> 00:49:19.032
It is, we should say that

00:49:19.232 --> 00:49:25.310
God is the one who is

00:49:28.454 --> 00:49:31.134
the Divinity, we can call it Divinity.

00:49:31.334 --> 00:49:34.404
And the Divinity becomes active.

00:49:34.694 --> 00:49:37.419
It sleeps, and then it becomes active.

00:49:37.619 --> 00:49:39.763
When it becomes active,

00:49:39.964 --> 00:49:44.453
then we say that God is now awakened.

00:49:44.654 --> 00:49:46.927
And when it is awakened,

00:49:47.128 --> 00:49:51.419
He separates Himself from His Power;

00:49:51.620 --> 00:49:54.984
and His Power is the Primordial Mother

00:49:55.184 --> 00:49:57.453
as we call Her, or the Holy Ghost.

00:49:57.654 --> 00:50:02.164
And He is watching the work of the Holy Ghost.

00:50:02.614 --> 00:50:05.653
She creates everything,

00:50:05.854 --> 00:50:09.244
She creates up to human beings,

00:50:09.734 --> 00:50:14.284
and it is He who is watching it. He is the spectator.

00:50:15.084 --> 00:50:16.853
There are many things can be said,

00:50:17.054 --> 00:50:20.584
because you see, God cannot be described in such a short time.

00:50:20.854 --> 00:50:22.764
But once you get your Realization

00:50:22.964 --> 00:50:25.934
you start understanding what is God Almighty

00:50:26.134 --> 00:50:27.509
and what is His Power.

00:50:27.710 --> 00:50:29.744
But first you must have the light.

00:50:29.944 --> 00:50:34.253
As I told you yesterday, now there are so many lights in this hall.

00:50:34.454 --> 00:50:36.004
Now if I start telling you

00:50:36.204 --> 00:50:38.914
about the origin of this light and electricity

00:50:39.114 --> 00:50:42.023
and how it came here and all that, it’s a headache.

00:50:42.224 --> 00:50:43.814
But what you have to do

00:50:44.014 --> 00:50:47.173
is to just put on one switch and it comes up.

00:50:47.374 --> 00:50:50.384
When you have the light, in that light if you see,

00:50:50.584 --> 00:50:53.623
this subtle knowledge will be easily understood.

00:50:53.824 --> 00:50:55.574
I am surprised that these people,

00:50:55.774 --> 00:50:58.773
who have never heard a name of Kundalini

00:50:58.974 --> 00:51:02.763
and who had no idea of Divinity also much,

00:51:02.964 --> 00:51:06.368
have become such experts in this knowledge, in such a short time,

00:51:06.569 --> 00:51:08.904
while it’s a very, very subtle knowledge.

00:51:09.455 --> 00:51:12.573
So gradually you will know everything.

00:51:12.774 --> 00:51:15.627
First you get your Realization.

00:51:16.807 --> 00:51:18.483
Now, again.

00:51:18.684 --> 00:51:22.294
I just wanted to respond to what You said.

00:51:24.096 --> 00:51:27.128
The response we have among people is very similar

00:51:27.329 --> 00:51:29.054
to what You say, in terms of

00:51:29.254 --> 00:51:31.464
“I don’t know of anybody else who is able to…”

00:51:31.665 --> 00:51:34.023
- Really? That’s all right.
So what it is?

00:51:34.224 --> 00:51:37.610
Yes, I really, I must tell you that they,

00:51:37.840 --> 00:51:41.229
I think these people understood there’s a market,

00:51:41.430 --> 00:51:45.453
because, you see, this is a special category of people you are.

00:51:45.654 --> 00:51:48.004
It's a special category, it's already described

00:51:48.204 --> 00:51:51.843
as such a special category of people who will seek God

00:51:52.044 --> 00:51:54.763
- they are called as “men of God” by William Blake -

00:51:54.964 --> 00:51:56.435
will be on this Earth

00:51:56.636 --> 00:52:01.034
and they will know God,

00:52:01.244 --> 00:52:03.704
also they will make others men of God.

00:52:03.904 --> 00:52:07.538
This is described. So many of them have prophesized like that.

00:52:08.212 --> 00:52:11.664
But when they came to know about that such a thing exists,

00:52:11.864 --> 00:52:14.304
they just started a market.

00:52:19.492 --> 00:52:24.130
I'm still confused. I have a connection with someone in India,

00:52:24.331 --> 00:52:28.054
by name [Shri Shritagu Balak Brahmachari]

00:52:28.254 --> 00:52:29.370
What is he saying?

00:52:29.571 --> 00:52:31.363
and he responds in a similar way.

00:52:31.564 --> 00:52:34.344
He has a connection with somebody in India

00:52:34.544 --> 00:52:36.804
who speaks in a similar way

00:52:37.004 --> 00:52:38.737
about these things to Yourself.

00:52:38.938 --> 00:52:43.344
He's confused as to who are the genuine and who are the...

00:52:43.574 --> 00:52:47.552
You see, the genuineness is first to apply one thing,

00:52:47.753 --> 00:52:49.655
does he take money, first?

00:52:49.855 --> 00:52:52.423
Ninety-nine percent they’ll finished.

00:52:52.624 --> 00:52:56.724
Then you should say, does he give Realization to his disciples?

00:52:56.984 --> 00:52:59.504
You talk to the disciples. Have they got their Realization?

00:52:59.704 --> 00:53:01.413
Have they got any knowledge?

00:53:01.614 --> 00:53:03.764
They know the modus operandi or not?

00:53:03.964 --> 00:53:06.058
If they do not know, just

00:53:06.259 --> 00:53:08.654
they said, “Now, you are realized”, that’s not.

00:53:08.854 --> 00:53:10.314
They have to know each and everything.

00:53:10.515 --> 00:53:12.443
What is their depth of knowledge?

00:53:12.644 --> 00:53:15.673
First, as you go in the market, you see, find out

00:53:15.874 --> 00:53:18.703
so if somebody has purchased something, is it good,

00:53:18.904 --> 00:53:20.504
is really good, or not?

00:53:20.704 --> 00:53:23.804
In the same way when you are seeking something,

00:53:24.004 --> 00:53:26.733
you must first really with a free mind

00:53:26.934 --> 00:53:30.193
go and see the disciples, what have they got,

00:53:30.394 --> 00:53:32.123
what have they achieved,

00:53:32.324 --> 00:53:36.362
how are they, what sort of a life they are leading?

00:53:36.563 --> 00:53:39.604
It’s the best way if you want to really find out,

00:53:39.804 --> 00:53:42.483
it’s the best way to do that.

00:53:42.684 --> 00:53:45.543
You should not just blindly go to something,

00:53:45.744 --> 00:53:48.523
and you should not just succumb to something

00:53:48.724 --> 00:53:49.912
because somebody says so.

00:53:50.113 --> 00:53:52.054
Even I, whatever I have said it,

00:53:52.255 --> 00:53:54.254
I said that you first experience.

00:53:54.484 --> 00:53:56.204
If you have the experience,

00:53:56.404 --> 00:53:58.304
then only you have to believe in yourself

00:53:58.504 --> 00:53:59.944
and you believe in Sahaja Yoga.

00:54:00.164 --> 00:54:03.424
Not before that. It’s a blindness.

00:54:03.625 --> 00:54:06.934
But you can't have the experience unless you have the connection.

00:54:07.135 --> 00:54:08.220
- What’s he saying?

00:54:08.421 --> 00:54:10.684
That's  what we are here for tonight to give you that thing.

00:54:10.884 --> 00:54:12.936
Of course, now I am going to do it.

00:54:13.137 --> 00:54:14.999
Just go on saying. Do you remember what people said?

00:54:15.200 --> 00:54:16.354
Please say that I would like to finish,

00:54:16.555 --> 00:54:19.207
- What’s he saying?
and just give me the experience.

00:54:20.083 --> 00:54:22.040
- Can I answer that Shri Mataji?
- Yes.

00:54:22.241 --> 00:54:24.804
- That is exactly what we will give you.

00:54:25.004 --> 00:54:27.365
You see, Shri Mataji will give you that experience

00:54:27.565 --> 00:54:30.773
and then you can make connections [to upon].

00:54:30.974 --> 00:54:34.333
You are making the connections through that experience.

00:54:34.534 --> 00:54:36.022
- All right.
- That's not something

00:54:36.222 --> 00:54:37.878
that you have to believe or something you will favour...

00:54:38.079 --> 00:54:39.164
No, no, no.

00:54:39.364 --> 00:54:41.923
No, no, no. Not at all it’s not thing like that.

00:54:42.124 --> 00:54:44.134
You have to certify yourself.

00:54:44.334 --> 00:54:45.664
Now the experience is

00:54:45.865 --> 00:54:47.343
that you feel the cool breeze

00:54:47.543 --> 00:54:50.593
coming out of your fontanel bone area

00:54:50.794 --> 00:54:52.493
yourself.

00:54:52.694 --> 00:54:56.734
And also you feel the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost all around you.

00:54:57.684 --> 00:55:00.659
This is to be certified by you only.

00:55:00.860 --> 00:55:03.654
But you should not also doubt yourself.

00:55:03.854 --> 00:55:05.364
Even so many feel, they'll say,

00:55:05.564 --> 00:55:08.574
“This is due to this air-conditioning.”

00:55:08.784 --> 00:55:11.983
Then they go home, close the windows, close the doors,

00:55:12.184 --> 00:55:14.493
make it hermetically sealed. Still they feel.

00:55:14.694 --> 00:55:17.187
Then they say, “Now what is this?”

00:55:17.651 --> 00:55:20.164
So doubting up to a point is sensible,

00:55:20.364 --> 00:55:21.955
but if you go beyond that

00:55:22.156 --> 00:55:24.631
then it’s harmful to you, not to anyone.

00:55:24.832 --> 00:55:28.378
Because I don’t need Sahaja Yoga, you need it.

00:55:30.694 --> 00:55:32.603
You need it.

00:55:32.804 --> 00:55:36.054
You want it, you have to ask for it.

00:55:36.694 --> 00:55:40.224
I cannot force on you. No, no, no way I can force you.

00:55:40.538 --> 00:55:43.453
You have to say “I want my Self-Realization.”

00:55:43.654 --> 00:55:45.405
In your freedom you have to ask,

00:55:45.606 --> 00:55:49.024
otherwise I cannot force. It cannot be forced.

00:55:49.972 --> 00:55:53.574
Now one more question and then we will start the...

00:55:53.974 --> 00:55:55.951
See person [started].

00:56:00.922 --> 00:56:02.244
I'm sorry.

00:56:02.445 --> 00:56:07.022
Can healing capacity is aligned to ayurvedic medicine?

00:56:07.223 --> 00:56:09.196
So is usual...

00:56:09.396 --> 00:56:13.664
Is the healing capacity of Sahaja Yoga

00:56:13.864 --> 00:56:16.664
aligned to ayurvedic medicine?

00:56:16.864 --> 00:56:18.554
What medicine?

00:56:18.764 --> 00:56:23.383
Is the ability of Sahaja Yoga to heal

00:56:23.584 --> 00:56:26.323
in any way connected with ayurvedic medicine?

00:56:26.524 --> 00:56:29.414
Of course. There are two doctors

00:56:29.614 --> 00:56:32.933
who have got their M.D. in Delhi,

00:56:33.134 --> 00:56:34.374
in Sahaja Yoga.

00:56:34.574 --> 00:56:37.240
They have shown how certain diseases are cured.

00:56:37.441 --> 00:56:40.163
They have taken three, four diseases, each person;

00:56:40.364 --> 00:56:41.772
Now there’s third one who’s doing.

00:56:41.973 --> 00:56:43.926
And there are seven doctors in London

00:56:44.126 --> 00:56:45.803
who are doing experiments.

00:56:46.004 --> 00:56:47.924
I mean, they are just trying to document it.

00:56:48.124 --> 00:56:49.784
Those people have been cured.

00:56:49.984 --> 00:56:54.974
There are people, like blood cancers, nephritis, myelitis,

00:56:55.174 --> 00:56:57.333
all kinds of people have been cured,

00:56:57.534 --> 00:56:59.774
So they are trying to document it.

00:56:59.974 --> 00:57:02.613
We have two hundred no, how many?

00:57:02.813 --> 00:57:05.483
Four hundred doctors in Russia

00:57:05.684 --> 00:57:07.623
who are practicing Sahaja Yoga.

00:57:07.879 --> 00:57:09.824
It’s all related to it.

00:57:10.624 --> 00:57:12.904
Because this is a new science, we can call it,

00:57:13.104 --> 00:57:15.893
this is Meta-modernism,

00:57:16.094 --> 00:57:19.223
when people are seeing something higher.

00:57:19.424 --> 00:57:21.774
It is working out.

00:57:23.261 --> 00:57:24.364
But that doesn’t mean

00:57:24.565 --> 00:57:26.427
that we’ll take away all the practice of doctors.

00:57:26.628 --> 00:57:28.265
They should not be afraid of it.

00:57:28.465 --> 00:57:31.103
Because, you see,

00:57:31.304 --> 00:57:34.583
we can only help people who get Realization,

00:57:34.784 --> 00:57:37.214
not the people who do not get Realization.

00:57:37.424 --> 00:57:40.863
Those people who do not get Realization, we cannot help them.

00:57:41.064 --> 00:57:44.464
So it is a by-product of your Realization.

00:57:54.974 --> 00:57:58.934
Reincarnation, Shri Mataji. What are Your thoughts he's asking.

00:57:59.204 --> 00:58:03.204
Reincarnation. What are Your thoughts on reincarnation?

00:58:04.544 --> 00:58:08.524
You do reincarnate, no doubt, you do.

00:58:08.915 --> 00:58:10.684
But you should not believe whatever I say.

00:58:10.885 --> 00:58:12.642
Why should you believe that?

00:58:12.843 --> 00:58:15.933
Because I am saying that? You should find out yourself.

00:58:16.134 --> 00:58:17.944
You can find out in Sahaja Yoga

00:58:18.144 --> 00:58:21.014
whatever I say is true or not.

00:58:23.936 --> 00:58:25.974
Whatever I say

00:58:27.194 --> 00:58:30.164
is for you to judge later on.

00:58:32.144 --> 00:58:35.324
It’s all absolutely open.

00:58:42.124 --> 00:58:46.057
The biggest thing that Sahaja Yoga has achieved, I feel,

00:58:46.258 --> 00:58:48.043
more than medical,

00:58:48.244 --> 00:58:53.804
is that they are absolutely free of addictions.

00:58:54.814 --> 00:58:56.923
People who came to Me

00:58:57.124 --> 00:59:04.153
were so addicted to such horrible type of drugs,

00:59:04.354 --> 00:59:07.123
that when they came they couldn’t see Me even.

00:59:07.324 --> 00:59:09.244
They were like coma patients.

00:59:09.445 --> 00:59:11.783
And overnight they gave it up.

00:59:11.984 --> 00:59:15.184
This is the biggest achievement today, I think.

00:59:17.624 --> 00:59:20.083
And I feel very gratified for that,

00:59:20.284 --> 00:59:23.064
because you must have heard how even small children

00:59:23.264 --> 00:59:26.134
below twelve years of age in England,

00:59:26.474 --> 00:59:29.849
in one part of England, in the southern part,

00:59:30.049 --> 00:59:31.444
are taking drugs,

00:59:31.645 --> 00:59:34.414
which is such a dangerous thing.

00:59:40.648 --> 00:59:43.863
Because you become absolutely free,

00:59:44.064 --> 00:59:48.094
and capable of asserting your freedom.

00:59:52.364 --> 00:59:57.384
Should we now have our Self-Realization, all of us?

01:00:12.409 --> 01:00:14.966
Before we start,

01:00:15.166 --> 01:00:20.244
I have to request you to take out your shoes,

01:00:20.444 --> 01:00:23.784
because this Mother Earth helps us a lot.

01:00:38.909 --> 01:00:41.475
Not working?

01:00:41.675 --> 01:00:43.944
All right.

01:00:44.747 --> 01:00:46.723
Now, it's all right.

01:00:46.924 --> 01:00:50.554
Connections, you see, that’s the point!

01:00:54.984 --> 01:00:57.824
Now there are two conditions

01:00:59.024 --> 01:01:01.529
which you have to accept.

01:01:02.234 --> 01:01:07.450
First one is that at this moment you forget the past.

01:01:07.651 --> 01:01:10.450
Absolutely,

01:01:11.984 --> 01:01:14.885
you should know that

01:01:15.139 --> 01:01:19.083
you have no business to condemn yourself,

01:01:21.335 --> 01:01:26.287
that you are not guilty at all of anything.

01:01:26.704 --> 01:01:29.583
If you feel guilty,

01:01:29.784 --> 01:01:32.374
then it’s another myth.

01:01:34.184 --> 01:01:36.813
And at this time

01:01:37.014 --> 01:01:40.303
you have to know this All-pervading Power

01:01:40.504 --> 01:01:43.043
is the ocean of forgiveness,

01:01:43.244 --> 01:01:46.284
and you cannot commit any mistakes

01:01:46.484 --> 01:01:49.743
which cannot be completely dissolved by this Power.

01:01:49.950 --> 01:01:52.495
So have confidence in yourself, please.

01:01:52.696 --> 01:01:55.084
These are very important conditions.

01:01:55.334 --> 01:01:57.064
Yesterday I met all of you,

01:01:57.264 --> 01:02:00.077
but today I may not be able to meet you all.

01:02:00.684 --> 01:02:04.374
At least those whom I’ve met yesterday must have noticed that

01:02:04.744 --> 01:02:09.063
I had to really correct them on these two points.

01:02:09.264 --> 01:02:12.604
So please help Me, cooperate.

01:02:13.974 --> 01:02:19.493
Then secondly, the second condition is very simple,

01:02:19.694 --> 01:02:22.483
if you understand

01:02:22.684 --> 01:02:29.896
that you have to forgive everyone, in general.

01:02:30.097 --> 01:02:33.816
Because logically, whether you forgive or don’t forgive,

01:02:34.017 --> 01:02:36.981
you don’t do anything. Logically, think about it.

01:02:37.182 --> 01:02:39.001
You don’t do anything,

01:02:39.202 --> 01:02:42.363
whether we forgive or we don’t forgive.

01:02:42.564 --> 01:02:45.152
But if we don’t forgive,

01:02:45.353 --> 01:02:48.001
then we play into wrong hands.

01:02:48.202 --> 01:02:51.934
The people who have tortured us or troubled us or hurt us

01:02:52.134 --> 01:02:54.255
are quite happy, but we are the ones,

01:02:54.456 --> 01:02:57.833
by not forgiving are suffering.

01:02:58.033 --> 01:02:59.688
Now some people say it’s very difficult,

01:02:59.889 --> 01:03:01.603
but it is just a myth,

01:03:01.804 --> 01:03:04.304
it’s just a bubble in your head.

01:03:04.904 --> 01:03:06.894
So just forgive all of them, once for all.

01:03:07.094 --> 01:03:09.544
I told yesterday those people who were not forgiving,

01:03:09.744 --> 01:03:11.004
they got their Realization,

01:03:11.204 --> 01:03:13.934
“Tell all the flowers, all the trees and everyone,

01:03:14.134 --> 01:03:15.764
loudly".

01:03:16.174 --> 01:03:18.244
Don’t think about them also individually.

01:03:18.444 --> 01:03:22.577
Just say “All of them I have forgiven, in general”.

01:03:23.164 --> 01:03:27.484
It’s such a relief. Immediately you’ll feel the relief on your head.

01:03:28.104 --> 01:03:30.964
It’s very important to forgive.

01:03:33.004 --> 01:03:35.564
And that you must have full confidence

01:03:35.765 --> 01:03:39.507
that you are all human beings, and you all are capable

01:03:39.708 --> 01:03:42.284
of getting Self-Realization.

01:03:43.654 --> 01:03:45.903
And “I will get my Realization”,

01:03:46.118 --> 01:03:49.570
that should be your

01:03:51.415 --> 01:03:56.149
full self-confidence. That is going to help us.

01:03:58.564 --> 01:04:01.904
Now as I have told you, that there’s left and right, two energies.

01:04:02.104 --> 01:04:07.383
The left is the energy of mundane desires,

01:04:07.584 --> 01:04:09.824
everyday desires, not the pure desire.

01:04:10.024 --> 01:04:13.264
And the right is the energy of action.

01:04:14.214 --> 01:04:17.763
So you please put both your feet

01:04:17.964 --> 01:04:21.444
little apart from each other, who are sitting on the chairs.

01:04:21.644 --> 01:04:23.881
Who are sitting on the ground are perfectly all right.

01:04:24.082 --> 01:04:26.063
They don’t have to worry.

01:04:26.264 --> 01:04:30.664
Now, please put your left hand towards Me.

01:04:31.814 --> 01:04:33.004
This is symbolic

01:04:33.204 --> 01:04:35.824
that you really want your Self-Realization.

01:04:36.564 --> 01:04:40.084
Those who do not want to have, I cannot force it on them

01:04:40.284 --> 01:04:42.264
and they should

01:04:43.374 --> 01:04:47.183
in all civility leave the hall,

01:04:47.384 --> 01:04:50.253
because they can disturb others’ ascent.

01:04:50.454 --> 01:04:53.400
So to be civil to others, they should leave the hall.

01:04:53.601 --> 01:04:56.444
But those who want to have their Self-Realization

01:04:56.644 --> 01:05:00.056
have to do this much, is

01:05:00.974 --> 01:05:03.862
to do what I’m telling you;

01:05:04.077 --> 01:05:09.236
and hardly ten minutes will take

01:05:09.437 --> 01:05:11.923
to have your Self-Realization.

01:05:12.124 --> 01:05:13.984
So just left hand towards Me,

01:05:14.185 --> 01:05:15.912
the right hand is to be used

01:05:16.113 --> 01:05:20.113
for nourishing your different centers.

01:05:20.314 --> 01:05:24.828
So you put first your right hand on your heart.

01:05:28.054 --> 01:05:33.594
This is the center of the Spirit.

01:05:33.804 --> 01:05:36.823
The Spirit resides in your heart,

01:05:37.024 --> 01:05:41.426
but its seat is here; but it resides in your heart.

01:05:42.884 --> 01:05:45.793
It resides in your heart.

01:05:45.994 --> 01:05:48.064
Then you take down your right hand

01:05:48.264 --> 01:05:51.124
in the upper portion of your abdomen.

01:05:52.684 --> 01:05:57.323
This is the center of your mastery,

01:05:57.524 --> 01:06:01.366
which has been created by great masters and prophets.

01:06:02.564 --> 01:06:04.528
Then you take down your right hand

01:06:04.729 --> 01:06:07.624
in the lower portion of your abdomen.

01:06:09.164 --> 01:06:12.922
This is the center of pure knowledge,

01:06:13.122 --> 01:06:14.803
absolute knowledge;

01:06:15.004 --> 01:06:18.004
knowledge about the divine powers,

01:06:18.204 --> 01:06:20.974
its laws, which work through your being.

01:06:21.174 --> 01:06:22.774
You don’t have to know mentally,

01:06:22.974 --> 01:06:26.203
but they are manifested through your being

01:06:26.404 --> 01:06:28.023
pure knowledge.

01:06:28.224 --> 01:06:30.387
As you can see Me,

01:06:30.587 --> 01:06:32.783
as you can feel something,

01:06:32.984 --> 01:06:36.984
in the same way, this pure knowledge works through you.

01:06:38.624 --> 01:06:42.489
Now raise your right hand in the upper portion of your abdomen.

01:06:46.334 --> 01:06:49.238
Then again on your heart.

01:06:50.564 --> 01:06:54.161
Then in the corner of your neck and your shoulder, as I told you,

01:06:54.362 --> 01:06:57.124
that when you feel guilty this center goes out of order,

01:06:57.324 --> 01:07:00.704
and turn your head to your right, completely.

01:07:03.904 --> 01:07:05.783
Here is the center where

01:07:05.984 --> 01:07:08.494
you have to forgive yourself completely,

01:07:08.694 --> 01:07:11.894
and to know that you are not guilty at all.

01:07:15.984 --> 01:07:20.603
Now take your right hand on your forehand across,

01:07:20.804 --> 01:07:25.564
like this, and gently put down your head as far as possible,

01:07:25.784 --> 01:07:28.124
resting on your hand.

01:07:29.674 --> 01:07:31.054
This is the center

01:07:31.255 --> 01:07:35.429
where you have to forgive everyone in general.

01:07:38.654 --> 01:07:42.101
Now you have to take your right hand on the back side of your head,

01:07:42.301 --> 01:07:43.679
back side of your head,

01:07:43.880 --> 01:07:46.853
and push back your head as far as possible.

01:07:47.054 --> 01:07:50.491
Push it back as far as possible.

01:07:53.044 --> 01:07:57.484
This is the center where, without feeling guilty,

01:07:57.684 --> 01:07:59.864
without counting your mistakes

01:08:00.064 --> 01:08:04.896
you have to ask forgiveness from the Divine Power.

01:08:05.764 --> 01:08:09.344
Now stretch your palm. I’m just telling you how to do it;

01:08:09.544 --> 01:08:11.734
then later on we’ll do it in a proper way.

01:08:11.934 --> 01:08:14.553
Now stretch your palm fully,

01:08:14.753 --> 01:08:18.960
and put the center of your palm

01:08:19.161 --> 01:08:21.963
exactly on the fontanel bone area,

01:08:22.164 --> 01:08:25.384
which was the soft bone in your childhood.

01:08:26.024 --> 01:08:30.244
Now please put down your head as far as possible,

01:08:30.854 --> 01:08:32.350
please put it down,

01:08:32.551 --> 01:08:38.493
and now start moving your scalp.

01:08:38.694 --> 01:08:41.454
Push back your fingers, otherwise there’s no proper pressure.

01:08:41.655 --> 01:08:43.844
Please push back your fingers nicely.

01:08:44.044 --> 01:08:46.863
Now move your scalp with that pressure

01:08:47.064 --> 01:08:49.333
not the hand so much as the scalp

01:08:49.534 --> 01:08:51.764
seven times, clockwise.

01:08:51.984 --> 01:08:55.223
Put down your head please, push back your fingers,

01:08:55.424 --> 01:09:00.164
and move your scalp slowly seven times.

01:09:03.464 --> 01:09:05.670
Very slowly,

01:09:08.715 --> 01:09:11.154
with a proper pressure.

01:09:25.203 --> 01:09:28.691
Done. That’s all we have to do.

01:09:28.892 --> 01:09:32.374
Now I will request you to take out your spectacles

01:09:32.574 --> 01:09:34.863
because you have to close your eyes,

01:09:35.064 --> 01:09:39.864
and till I tell you, please don’t open your eyes.

01:09:41.134 --> 01:09:45.032
Move your legs apart from each other,

01:09:45.233 --> 01:09:51.003
and please put your left hand towards Me

01:09:51.204 --> 01:09:53.903
and right hand on your heart,

01:09:54.104 --> 01:09:57.804
and now, if there is anything

01:09:58.004 --> 01:10:01.599
that is tight on your neck or on your waist,

01:10:01.800 --> 01:10:06.571
please reduce the pressure, be comfortable,

01:10:06.772 --> 01:10:11.158
sit straight, not too much bending or bending back

01:10:11.359 --> 01:10:15.194
but in a comfortable way, in a very comfortable way.

01:10:15.464 --> 01:10:20.116
Now, you have to be pleasantly placed towards yourself.

01:10:23.124 --> 01:10:27.413
Now, please put your right hand on your heart.

01:10:45.090 --> 01:10:46.945
Here you have to ask Me

01:10:47.146 --> 01:10:50.414
a very fundamental question about yourself,

01:10:51.338 --> 01:10:54.444
because I told you, you have to become a divine computer.

01:10:54.644 --> 01:10:57.104
So first you use Me for that.

01:10:57.304 --> 01:11:00.174
Now ask a question, in your heart -

01:11:00.374 --> 01:11:04.294
you can call Me “Shri Mataji” or “Mother” whatever you like -

01:11:04.694 --> 01:11:06.694
ask a question three times,

01:11:06.904 --> 01:11:10.334
“Mother, am I the Spirit?” Ask sincerely.

01:11:10.534 --> 01:11:14.185
“Mother, am I the Spirit?” Ask three times.

01:11:34.441 --> 01:11:37.099
Now,

01:11:43.024 --> 01:11:45.614
if you are the Spirit,

01:11:45.814 --> 01:11:47.364
you are your master,

01:11:47.564 --> 01:11:50.971
because in that light you know,

01:11:51.172 --> 01:11:53.563
what is right, what is wrong,

01:11:53.764 --> 01:11:55.804
and you become your own guide.

01:11:56.014 --> 01:11:57.384
So now put your right hand

01:11:57.584 --> 01:12:00.214
in the upper portion of your abdomen, on the left-hand side.

01:12:00.414 --> 01:12:03.157
We are only working on the left-hand side.

01:12:03.358 --> 01:12:06.203
Press it hard. And here

01:12:06.404 --> 01:12:09.846
you ask another question three times,

01:12:10.077 --> 01:12:14.904
“Mother, am I my own master?”

01:12:15.104 --> 01:12:17.453
Ask this question three times,

01:12:17.884 --> 01:12:22.264
“Mother, am I my own master?”

01:12:24.564 --> 01:12:30.303
I have already told you that I respect your freedom.

01:12:30.504 --> 01:12:35.313
I cannot force pure knowledge upon you.

01:12:36.974 --> 01:12:39.323
So now please put your right hand

01:12:39.524 --> 01:12:42.363
in the lower portion of your abdomen.

01:12:42.624 --> 01:12:49.717
Here you have to ask, three times,

01:12:51.174 --> 01:12:53.342
six times, because this petal,

01:12:53.542 --> 01:12:56.733
this, this center has got six petals.

01:12:56.934 --> 01:13:00.094
Please ask six times,

01:13:01.044 --> 01:13:07.124
“Mother, please give me pure knowledge.”

01:13:07.324 --> 01:13:09.094
Please say that six times,

01:13:09.294 --> 01:13:12.444
“Mother, please give me pure knowledge.”

01:13:12.644 --> 01:13:17.063
Say it in humility; you are asking for the highest.

01:13:17.264 --> 01:13:20.164
Six times, please.

01:13:41.624 --> 01:13:44.643
When you ask for pure knowledge

01:13:44.844 --> 01:13:47.563
your Kundalini starts rising.

01:13:47.764 --> 01:13:50.654
So we have to clear our upper centers

01:13:50.854 --> 01:13:54.953
with our self-confidence.

01:13:55.154 --> 01:13:56.484
So raise your right hand

01:13:56.685 --> 01:13:59.364
in the upper portion of your abdomen, on the left-hand side,

01:13:59.564 --> 01:14:01.654
and here you press it hard

01:14:01.855 --> 01:14:07.483
and say with full confidence ten times, ten times,

01:14:07.684 --> 01:14:11.264
“Mother, I am my own master”.

01:14:11.464 --> 01:14:14.573
“Mother, I am my own master”.

01:14:14.774 --> 01:14:16.574
Please say.

01:14:19.344 --> 01:14:21.884
Ten times.

01:14:35.534 --> 01:14:36.894
As I told you

01:14:37.094 --> 01:14:41.684
that you are not this body, this mind, this ego,

01:14:41.884 --> 01:14:43.913
these conditionings,

01:14:44.114 --> 01:14:49.321
but you are the pure Spirit.

01:14:50.243 --> 01:14:55.704
So now please raise your right hand on your heart.

01:14:56.734 --> 01:15:01.364
Here now, say with full confidence, twelve times,

01:15:01.604 --> 01:15:04.984
“Mother, I am the pure Spirit”.

01:15:05.194 --> 01:15:07.904
Please say it twelve times,

01:15:08.124 --> 01:15:12.383
“Mother, I am the pure Spirit”.

01:15:12.584 --> 01:15:15.840
Please put your hand on your heart.

01:15:18.734 --> 01:15:21.043
This divine Power,

01:15:21.244 --> 01:15:24.253
is the ocean of knowledge,

01:15:24.454 --> 01:15:28.852
is the ocean of love, compassion and bliss;

01:15:29.053 --> 01:15:33.284
but above all it is the ocean of forgiveness,

01:15:33.574 --> 01:15:36.164
and you can not commit any mistakes

01:15:36.374 --> 01:15:39.068
which cannot be dissolved

01:15:39.269 --> 01:15:43.673
by this great power of forgiveness.

01:15:44.834 --> 01:15:47.223
So please forgive yourself,

01:15:47.424 --> 01:15:51.694
and put your hand in the corner of your neck and your shoulder,

01:15:51.894 --> 01:15:54.453
and turn your head to your right.

01:15:54.654 --> 01:15:57.048
Here, please help Me,

01:15:57.249 --> 01:15:59.564
by saying with full confidence,

01:15:59.764 --> 01:16:03.639
“Mother, I am not guilty at all”.

01:16:03.840 --> 01:16:08.066
Just say that, with full confidence, please.

01:16:20.214 --> 01:16:23.865
You have to say that, please,

01:16:24.066 --> 01:16:26.740
sixteen times.

01:16:31.691 --> 01:16:33.743
I have already told you

01:16:33.944 --> 01:16:38.029
that if you forgive or don’t forgive,

01:16:38.230 --> 01:16:41.798
you do not do anything. It’s a myth,

01:16:41.999 --> 01:16:43.181
absolute myth.

01:16:43.382 --> 01:16:45.333
But if you don’t forgive,

01:16:45.534 --> 01:16:50.303
then you play into wrong hands and torture yourself.

01:16:50.504 --> 01:16:52.587
So give up this myth, once for all,

01:16:52.788 --> 01:16:55.044
just give up this myth!

01:16:55.654 --> 01:16:58.146
Now raise your right hand

01:16:58.347 --> 01:17:01.470
onto your forehead across,

01:17:01.671 --> 01:17:06.015
and put down your head as far as possible.

01:17:07.024 --> 01:17:12.614
Now, here, you have to say, not how many times but with

01:17:14.394 --> 01:17:16.763
your heart in it.

01:17:16.978 --> 01:17:19.243
Say it,

01:17:19.444 --> 01:17:25.663
“Mother, I forgive everyone in general.”

01:17:25.864 --> 01:17:28.234
Just say that,

01:17:30.794 --> 01:17:33.654
from your heart.

01:17:53.074 --> 01:17:58.193
Now take back your right hand on the back side of your head,

01:17:58.394 --> 01:18:02.684
and push back your head as far as possible.

01:18:06.664 --> 01:18:08.474
Here,

01:18:10.854 --> 01:18:12.784
without feeling guilty,

01:18:12.984 --> 01:18:14.644
without counting your mistakes,

01:18:14.844 --> 01:18:16.824
just for your satisfaction,

01:18:17.444 --> 01:18:19.593
you have to say

01:18:19.794 --> 01:18:23.304
from your heart, not how many times,

01:18:24.124 --> 01:18:25.794
“Oh divine Power,

01:18:25.994 --> 01:18:29.402
if I have done any mistakes knowingly or unknowingly,

01:18:29.603 --> 01:18:31.524
please forgive me”.

01:18:32.114 --> 01:18:33.904
Say it from your heart,

01:18:34.104 --> 01:18:35.554
“Oh divine Power,

01:18:35.754 --> 01:18:40.570
if I have done anything, against you or any mistakes,

01:18:40.771 --> 01:18:42.863
please forgive me”.

01:18:43.064 --> 01:18:46.484
That’s all you have to say, from your heart.

01:18:47.664 --> 01:18:51.334
Stretch back your head, fully.

01:18:58.954 --> 01:19:02.884
Now, stretch your hand fully.

01:19:21.574 --> 01:19:25.764
And put the center of your palm

01:19:25.964 --> 01:19:30.933
on top of your fontanel bone area,

01:19:31.134 --> 01:19:35.696
which was a soft bone in your childhood.

01:19:46.564 --> 01:19:52.705
Now, bend your head as far as possible.

01:19:54.314 --> 01:19:57.538
Now, push back your fingers,

01:19:57.738 --> 01:20:01.174
to have a good pressure on your scalp.

01:20:02.214 --> 01:20:05.253
Here again, I cannot force

01:20:05.454 --> 01:20:09.493
Self-Realization on you, I cannot force.

01:20:09.694 --> 01:20:13.033
So you have to ask for it.

01:20:13.234 --> 01:20:17.994
Now move your scalp slowly, seven times,

01:20:19.554 --> 01:20:21.623
saying seven times,

01:20:21.824 --> 01:20:25.324
“Mother, please give me Self-Realization”,

01:20:25.554 --> 01:20:27.774
saying seven times,

01:20:27.974 --> 01:20:32.054
“Mother, please give me Self-Realization”.

01:21:21.414 --> 01:21:24.139
Please open your eyes, slowly.

01:21:24.340 --> 01:21:27.417
Put down your hands.

01:21:29.387 --> 01:21:33.654
Now please put both your hands towards Me, like this.

01:21:37.772 --> 01:21:42.483
Put your right hand towards Me, like this,

01:21:42.684 --> 01:21:45.613
and now put down your head,

01:21:45.814 --> 01:21:49.733
and see if you are getting yourself

01:21:49.934 --> 01:21:54.876
a cool or a hot breeze coming out of your fontanel bone area.

01:21:55.077 --> 01:21:57.460
Just see for yourself.

01:21:58.694 --> 01:22:02.614
Now don’t put the hand on top of your head, but away from it.

01:22:02.814 --> 01:22:06.124
And sometimes you might get it much further.

01:22:06.324 --> 01:22:09.734
You can also move your hand to see

01:22:10.344 --> 01:22:13.343
if there’s a cool breeze coming out of your head.

01:22:13.544 --> 01:22:17.604
Now don’t doubt about the air-conditioner,

01:22:17.804 --> 01:22:21.127
because it’s coming out of your head.

01:22:23.274 --> 01:22:26.056
Now,

01:22:26.624 --> 01:22:29.784
put your left hand towards Me,

01:22:32.564 --> 01:22:35.663
and put down your head.

01:22:35.864 --> 01:22:39.284
And now see with your right hand, right hand,

01:22:39.484 --> 01:22:43.844
if you are getting a cool or a hot breeze

01:22:44.044 --> 01:22:47.915
out of your fontanel bone area.

01:22:52.344 --> 01:22:55.084
Now, again put your right hand towards Me,

01:22:55.284 --> 01:22:57.194
right hand like this.

01:22:57.694 --> 01:22:59.432
Put down your head.

01:22:59.662 --> 01:23:02.493
See for last time, see clearly,

01:23:02.694 --> 01:23:06.543
if there’s a cool or a hot breeze

01:23:06.744 --> 01:23:08.965
may be slight, might be more coming.

01:23:09.165 --> 01:23:10.923
Don’t get confused.

01:23:11.124 --> 01:23:14.375
See for yourself, your attention.

01:23:14.581 --> 01:23:16.890
It’s coming out.

01:23:19.364 --> 01:23:22.543
Now put both the hands towards Me like this,

01:23:22.744 --> 01:23:25.084
and watch Me without thinking.

01:23:25.284 --> 01:23:28.818
You will see that there’s no thought in your mind.

01:23:32.284 --> 01:23:35.053
Now raise both your hands

01:23:35.254 --> 01:23:38.028
towards the sky like this,

01:23:39.844 --> 01:23:43.024
and ask another fundamental question,

01:23:43.224 --> 01:23:45.838
“Mother, is this the...

01:23:46.045 --> 01:23:49.655
Mother is this the breeze,

01:23:52.314 --> 01:23:56.244
the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?"

01:23:58.424 --> 01:24:00.284
"Mother,

01:24:01.344 --> 01:24:06.173
is this the All-pervading Power of divine love?

01:24:06.374 --> 01:24:09.704
Mother, is this the Paramachaitanya?”

01:24:09.934 --> 01:24:12.064
Ask anyone of these questions three times.

01:24:12.264 --> 01:24:14.653
Put back your head completely.

01:24:14.854 --> 01:24:17.624
Push back your head completely,

01:24:17.864 --> 01:24:22.504
and ask this question, anyone of them, three times.

01:24:25.254 --> 01:24:26.840
Now take down your hands.

01:24:27.040 --> 01:24:29.777
Such flowing of vibrations!

01:24:35.334 --> 01:24:40.394
All those who have felt cool breeze on your fingertips,

01:24:40.684 --> 01:24:42.493
in your hands,

01:24:42.693 --> 01:24:48.273
or on top of your fontanel bone area,

01:24:48.474 --> 01:24:50.105
please raise both your hands.

01:24:50.306 --> 01:24:52.947
Please raise both your hands.

01:24:59.154 --> 01:25:01.964
May God bless you all.

01:25:03.924 --> 01:25:05.504
May God bless you all.

01:25:05.704 --> 01:25:07.633
Now you should know, it has not happened

01:25:07.834 --> 01:25:09.764
through any mental activity.

01:25:10.014 --> 01:25:12.464
So you cannot argue it out, you cannot discuss it,

01:25:12.664 --> 01:25:14.964
but you have to just feel it and grow into it.

01:25:15.194 --> 01:25:17.833
Another thing I would suggest that

01:25:18.034 --> 01:25:21.744
it’s not an individual procedure,

01:25:21.944 --> 01:25:24.884
it’s a collective procedure, it’s a collective thing.

01:25:25.084 --> 01:25:28.604
Like one nail, which falls out of your body,

01:25:28.804 --> 01:25:30.733
it’s not looked after. In the same way,

01:25:30.934 --> 01:25:33.684
if you say that “I am doing it at home, Mother, it’s all right”,

01:25:33.884 --> 01:25:36.793
that’s not the thing. You have to come to our collective.

01:25:36.994 --> 01:25:41.074
And we have a very nice collective arrangements here

01:25:41.304 --> 01:25:42.696
where you can come,

01:25:42.897 --> 01:25:44.913
and you can tell your problems,

01:25:45.114 --> 01:25:47.104
and you can master this art,

01:25:47.304 --> 01:25:48.724
absolutely master.

01:25:48.924 --> 01:25:51.874
I hope next year I’ll come to Melbourne

01:25:52.074 --> 01:25:54.204
and I’ll find lots of people

01:25:54.494 --> 01:25:56.654
who have achieved this mastery.

01:25:56.854 --> 01:25:58.924
I bless you all from My heart.

01:25:59.194 --> 01:26:01.324
Those who have not felt cool breeze

01:26:01.524 --> 01:26:02.764
can come on this side.

01:26:02.965 --> 01:26:04.964
So I may not be able to meet all of you,

01:26:05.164 --> 01:26:07.944
though I wanted very much to meet all of you today again,

01:26:08.144 --> 01:26:12.254
but we’ll have some music for you to enjoy. Please!

01:26:15.654 --> 01:26:17.494
Just....

01:26:23.338 --> 01:26:24.775
Sit down. Yes.

01:26:24.987 --> 01:26:27.154
Make a... We have a special announcement to make.

01:26:27.355 --> 01:26:29.815
So please, please.

01:26:37.513 --> 01:26:39.786
She wants what?

01:26:40.365 --> 01:26:41.990
I will follow.

01:26:42.190 --> 01:26:43.687
Water, all right, please come.

01:26:43.888 --> 01:26:46.705
Give her some. Is there any other glass?

01:26:47.495 --> 01:26:51.233
Some other glass. Just put some other glass, please.

01:26:54.374 --> 01:26:57.874
It’s difficult for Me.  It’s all right for a child.

01:27:24.052 --> 01:27:26.579
So, yes, how are you?

01:27:26.798 --> 01:27:30.183
Mother, they came for Sahaja Yoga in July,

01:27:30.383 --> 01:27:32.451
- They are here.
- Who?

01:27:32.674 --> 01:27:35.615
There is one with wheelchair and the one behind.

01:27:35.815 --> 01:27:37.901
- She's all right?
- Yes, she's there.

01:27:38.114 --> 01:27:40.827
- Ah, She is the one?
- The young, the young one there.

01:27:41.028 --> 01:27:43.824
- Yes, really! What trouble they had?

01:27:44.024 --> 01:27:45.644
That one was paralyzed.

01:27:45.844 --> 01:27:48.554
Now she can move left hand and the [right foot]...

01:27:48.844 --> 01:27:54.047
Amjad! Amjad! Doctor Amjad Ali, please come along.

01:27:54.603 --> 01:27:57.246
Are you here?

01:27:57.894 --> 01:27:59.380
We will just talk to them,

01:27:59.580 --> 01:28:01.223
and he has to take their,

01:28:01.424 --> 01:28:04.201
they must be having their medical reports.

01:28:04.408 --> 01:28:06.112
No, they haven't, because they live,

